A Jonatan\u233?m t\u233?mndang\u233? Deifid, "Y\u233?ndo efalo si norayan Yurane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan, Israil \u225?rfene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, nden\u233? y\u233?nam\u233? s\u233?nonjo efogh k\u233?t\u225?n kaitau, o \u225?mb efogh k\u233?tam\u233? soram\u233? y\u233?nd so noraiwam tane afaf\u233? a so mat k\u233?ny\u225?ton f\u233?yotio ndernaye f\u225? nemne fenem\u233?n. Njam f\u225? norayai fenem\u233?n m\u233?ndef\u233?, y\u233?ndo so k\u233?maufron. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
W\u233?nde f\u225? njam y\u233?m n\u233?kwaf\u233? a m\u233?nde y\u233?m siya n\u233?smeta f\u233?m k\u233?rotio fai Yuram kw\u233?smang\u233? y\u233?nd njam y\u233?ndon yau mat k\u233?ny\u225?ton f\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m so ngatno a gh\u233?rs\u233? m\u233? n\u233?ng\u233?m. So y\u233?m Yur\u233? fefaf nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u225? k\u233?s t\u233?morw\u233?n tane afafaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
A so f\u233?mo kor w\u233?frende y\u233?nd Yurane ndimbal uw\u233?ghe njamandio f\u233?m gh\u233?rs\u233? n\u233?m. W\u233?nde y\u233?nd njam k\u233?r w\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Kor efrenda tane m\u233?r\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? ndimbal uw\u233?ghe, ndemam\u233?n njam Yuram ewalinda m\u233?inyotio fene m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r k\u233?tam\u233? mbandta."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u233?yo Jonatanam yafrotam ambino mwigh\u233? y\u233?maf\u233? Deifidf\u233? korayau, "So Yuram tawalindang\u233? fene m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r!" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
F\u233?yo Jonatan\u233?m yiy\u225?toi Deifid w\u233?ikor mwigh\u233? t\u225?ik\u233?r y\u225?ne ufoghm\u233?n f\u250?taryamm\u233?n w\u233?ikor, m\u233?nam\u233?n Jonatan\u233?m tuwetau Deifid nden\u233? yame ndernaye f\u225?yo n\u225?uw\u233?te.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
A Jonatan norayai, "K\u225?ye y\u233?ndfem so yafrotam tot\u233?r gh\u233?rarem\u233?n t\u233?m\u233?nd. F\u233?m so n\u225?l\u225?ite njam fene sifay\u233? n\u225?l\u225?ita s\u233?kian. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Namb\u233?t f\u233?r\u233?gh\u233?tro, n\u233?ng\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n sifayat \u225?nde f\u233?m natnoi fronde, a nawanjeta k\u233?t\u233? w\u233?m rufruffaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Y\u233?nd so k\u233?ntor\u233?n a engwitan nambio fimb w\u233?m rufruf t\u233?ndota nden\u233? kar y\u233?ndo m\u233? wigh tangwitaw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?ndo so y\u233?ngwafaretan ambum m\u233?n\u225?t fimb so en\u233?rse a enwangota. Njam f\u233?mo wiy\u225?reta y\u233?nd t\u233?mnde f\u225?, "Y\u233?n\u233? em y\u233?n\u233? kar\u233?fta,' f\u233?yo f\u233?m mat so n\u233?m, nden\u233? n\u233?m\u233? w\u233?t Yur\u233? nakete, nden\u233? m\u233?inyotio merro y\u233?m, a yau y\u233?m \u225?mb k\u233?rt\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
W\u233?nde njam y\u233?ndo t\u233?mndan f\u225?, 'Kor nayu k\u233?ng\u233?m-fimb m\u233? enn\u233?m fefaf,' f\u233?yo Yuram f\u233?m n\u233?ngmatembete nayu. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
A so Yuram y\u233?ny\u225?tow\u233? yerwam t\u233?fenjo uny\u233?ghofnar so t\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n Yur\u233? t\u233? gh\u233?k\u233?f tawafayote.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
F\u233?yo Deifid natnoi yambia ndau sifayan, a njam tot\u233?r gh\u233?rarem\u233?n t\u233?m\u233?nd narnai warsagh \u225?r n\u225?mnjoi n\u233?net. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
F\u225? n\u225?mnjoi k\u233?tam\u233? y\u225?ne t\u250?m\u233?n \u225?mnjogh sifayata mbakwta, y\u233?maf\u233? Jonatan t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n y\u225? t\u233?ndota a Abna y\u225? kaka. W\u233?nde Deifidene sifay\u233? sotro t\u233?morw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Sol \u225?mb n\u233?m\u233? si yau norayai y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? efghon f\u225? m\u233? norayai y\u225?njo k\u233?nj\u250?nro, \u225?mb rokaram m\u233?t\u233? t\u225?f tiy\u225?tong\u233? Deifid t\u233?m\u233?nd yaman yau mer." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
W\u233?nde njam Deifidene sifay\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n sotro y\u233?namayo efghon, Sol\u233?m y\u233?motai Jonatan, "N\u233?mam\u233?n Jesene ambum y\u233?na yau y\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t njamke n\u233?net k\u225?ye w\u233?i yau a s\u233?nonjo?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Jonatan n\u233?ngwangoi, "Deifid\u233?m m\u233?njtaye w\u233?mota y\u233?nd njam t\u233? f\u225? kuwanong\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n Betliem\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
F\u225? norayai, ' Gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? kumyongi y\u233?nd so kuwanon, y\u233?ndfem yafrotam m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?n gh\u233?ng\u233?n. Tane an\u233? komnende nden\u233? y\u233?nd k\u233?t\u233? so w\u233?m. F\u233?yo gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? y\u233?nd so kit\u233?rmbon m\u233?n\u225?t so tawinjon tane anaf. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan f\u225? y\u233?na yau y\u233?m warsagh \u225?roene s\u233?kis\u233?kiyan."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Sol gh\u233?rgh\u233?r m\u233?ndm\u233?nd nawerai Jonatanefaf, "F\u233?m ndombanj\u233?r \u225?y\u225?r\u233?ghofnar amafoene ambum! Y\u233?mo tatembetau f\u225?. N\u233?m\u233? f\u233?m nemne y\u233?nd mafina w\u233?m nden\u233? f\u233?m m\u233?nde n\u233?m y\u225?faf siya y\u233?m warsagh \u225?rfene yuwon, w\u225?iw\u225?i efe f\u233?m a fetm\u233?? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? teke y\u233?n\u233? Jesene ambum k\u233?s gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?m, f\u233?m yau so warsagh \u225?r n\u233?m. Y\u233?nam\u233? kuwano a t\u233?r\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?ndo so k\u233?rotio t\u233?sman f\u225?!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
Jonatan\u233?m y\u233?motai, "W\u233?nde n\u233?mam\u233?n so f\u225? k\u233?rot t\u233?kmangi? N\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mo tafrote?" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
F\u233?yo Sol\u233?m yauyotam fimb t\u233?rametau m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i t\u233?smangai f\u225? k\u233?rotio. F\u233?yo soram\u233? Jonatan mat n\u225?y\u225?toi nden\u233? y\u225?refam f\u233?t\u233? mwighaye t\u233?kmai m\u233?n\u225?t k\u233?rotio so t\u233?smetau Deifid.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Jonatan\u233?m y\u233?frangoi s\u233?kis\u233?ki n\u233?kwaf\u233? a nakenai n\u233?net y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?namayom\u233?n efogh t\u233?mndan, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? y\u225?refane w\u225?iw\u225?iyaf\u233? yam k\u233?rt\u233? yam y\u233?tumndai y\u225?nem\u233?n Deifidem\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
Y\u233?nam\u233? y\u233?n\u233? nufrotam akwan nden\u233? Jonatan nuwanoi k\u233?t\u225?n ndau sifayat efalo \u225?rk\u233? yiy\u225?teyay\u233?nd Deifidf\u233?, a n\u233?mbnar ambumof\u233? tarw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
F\u225? norayai y\u225?njo ambum tosafaf, "Kengo, tawinjo s\u233?nonjo fimb \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? y\u233?ndon so eitan." Njam ambum tos\u233? k\u233?rsau, y\u233?mo yitam fimb y\u233?ngwaindam f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
Njam ambum tosam yiy\u225?njai fimboene sifay\u233? \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? Jonatan\u233?m \u233? y\u233?ngwitam, Jonatan n\u233?ngutnai ambum tos\u233? soram\u233? a n\u233?ngorayai, "N\u233?m\u233? fimb m\u233? soramayo y\u233?m feta?" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
A Jonatan n\u233?ngutnai ambum tos\u233? soramata, "W\u233?keye, w\u233?keye n\u233?m, yau t\u225?f n\u233?mor!" F\u233?yo Jonatanene ambum tosam y\u233?kafai fimb a y\u233?nmorm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n y\u225?njo ndimbaloefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
W\u233?nde ambum tos\u233? yau kemnau m\u233?nam\u233?n, m\u233? f\u225?ro Jonatan a Deifid mat tarw\u233?n k\u233?rtam\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
F\u233?yo Jonatan\u233?m yaramai y\u225?njo fimb y\u225?njo ambum tosai a norayai, "Kuwano en\u233?mnja f\u225? y\u233?nan ndimbal tesenot."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
Njam ambum tos\u233? n\u233?ngwanoi Deifid nokayoi naikai tambne a nuyai y\u225?njo s\u225?f k\u233?t\u225?n mbandot, a y\u225?wefnoi nambinotm\u233?. A nasnem\u233?nd f\u225? a ye m\u233?rne k\u233?ngw\u233?t, w\u233?nde Deifid mindefifi kendau.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
Jonatan norayai Deifidefaf, "N\u233?ng\u233?m \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233?, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?n\u233? n\u233?ndk\u233?fan f\u233?m a y\u233?nd a y\u233?n\u233? n\u233?ndk\u233?fan tane \u225?ki ambum a fene \u225?ki ambum tuot." F\u233?yo nokayoi a nuwanoi ndimbal tesen k\u233?nj\u250?t.
