F\u233?yo Deifid y\u233?nmorm\u233?n y\u233?nan Nob y\u225?faf Aimelek gh\u233?ng\u233?n warogh \u225?r, a Aimelek t\u233?morw\u233?n tik\u233?ftik\u233?fero a y\u233?fangoi Deifid a y\u233?mndai f\u225?, "N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m f\u233?mbia n\u233?m a \u225?mb \u225?rf\u233? yau ere?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Deifid norayai Aimelekefaf gh\u233?ng\u233?n warogh \u225?r, "Warsagh \u225?rom t\u233? waram \u225?s\u225?fogh k\u233?rtaf\u233? a t\u233? w\u233?mnde y\u233?nd, '\u193?rk\u233? \u225?r yau so mat k\u225?y\u225?tong\u233? y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?rtam\u233?n \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayan y\u233?ndon n\u233?ngmafaretan f\u233?m.' Y\u233?nayai y\u233?ndon ndernaye \u225?s\u225?fogh n\u233?maraman fem, a y\u233?ndo t\u233? tot\u233?r ambum tafaretan k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mb sifayat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?nam\u233? nden\u233?, n\u233?m\u233? fene ngangayan y\u233?m? Kwaram ta 5 f\u233?skaf flaw\u233? sut, o n\u233?m\u233? njam t\u233? tawinjon."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Gh\u233?ng\u233?n warogh \u225?rom yawangoi Deifide a norayai, "Yau y\u233?m m\u233?nd flaw\u233? ngangayan, w\u233?nde y\u233?na y\u233?m wateghkaf flaw\u233?, t\u225?f njam tot\u233?r ambum em nayu amafafeta."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Deifid\u233?m yawangoi, "Yau m\u225?m\u233? mwigh\u233? n\u233?m, y\u233?ndo yau eumyota tane \u225?r ghak\u233?r m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i em amafaf\u233? njam em m\u233?nayan misi \u225?s\u225?foghan. A f\u225? w\u233?i m\u233? emor merro t\u225?f m\u233?nd efogh \u225?ligh k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?, nder\u233? mindefifi so y\u233?m y\u233?nayan!" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u233?yo gh\u233?ng\u233?n warogh \u225?rom yaramai y\u225? wateghkaf flaw\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? yau \u225?mb flaw\u233? tamorw\u233?n w\u233?nde s\u225?f auyafogh flawaro \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? t\u233? ewimnday\u233?nd Yurane s\u225?fan, m\u233?n\u225?t so t\u233?kmangay\u233?nd waft\u233? flaw\u233? y\u225?ne sifayan njam t\u233?ngwanangay\u233?nd.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
