\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Deifid norayai Aimelekefaf, "S\u233?nonjo y\u233?nam\u233? t\u233? y\u233?m fimb a witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? n\u225?if\u233? ngangayan? Y\u233?ndon n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? \u225?mb y\u233?nmanam tane witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? n\u225?if\u233? yau \u225?mb y\u233?ndon m\u233?k rokaraf\u233?, m\u233?nam\u233?n warsagh \u225?roene k\u233?rt\u233? st\u233?morw\u233?n w\u233?kegheyot."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
F\u233?yo gh\u233?ng\u233?n warogh \u225?r norayai, "M\u233?n\u233? Goliatene witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? n\u225?if\u233? Filistainm\u233?n f\u233?mofem efe y\u233?smetam\u233?nd k\u233?rotio y\u233?n\u233? mband tunak\u233?f ewor\u233?gh sifayafaf Ela a y\u233?n\u233? fiyar\u233?ghkaf t\u233?morw\u233?n s\u225?l\u225?meye y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?ndota efod s\u225?l\u225?meta. Njam f\u233?mof\u233? tane fendio, t\u233?ngwan, m\u233?nam\u233?n nden\u233? \u225?mb yau y\u233?m tumyo y\u233?na." F\u233?yo Deifid norayai, nden\u233? \u225?mb yau y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m, kwaram ta."
