A, f\u233?m t\u233? ndimbal k\u233?r\u225?ye k\u233?n\u233?m gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsisaf\u233? tafaf s\u233?nonjo njam y\u233?n\u233? sifayan y\u233?ta Yuram w\u233?k\u233?m \u225?nde f\u233?mo y\u233?nd so kw\u233?smangai k\u233?rotio, w\u233?nde f\u233?mo yau tafrote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Emo \u225?mb so taumyong\u233? y\u225?ne m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r s\u225?i teghangi t\u225?f y\u225?faf njam y\u233?m y\u225?ne waft\u233?? So Yuram fai kemaramang\u233? fe mere m\u233?nam\u233?n fene gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsisam\u233?n \u225?rk\u233? tuyafote tafaf s\u233?nonjo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
A s\u233?nonjo y\u233?nd mat n\u225?y\u225?ton nden\u233? f\u233?m so n\u233?m warsagh \u225?r, a Israil \u225?rfene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh so marat n\u225?y\u225?tote fene lim\u225?n\u233?gh mbanmbanan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
S\u233?nonjo mbark\u225?nd si koraya tafaf Yurane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? njam nufrota f\u233?mo yau so esmete tane m\u233?r\u233?n a tawalinda tane \u225?ki ambum!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
F\u233?yo Deifid y\u233?n\u233? uny\u233?ghofnar si norayai y\u225?faf Solefaf kw\u233?rnar sie. F\u233?yo Sol n\u233?wanoi m\u233?ngotuot, w\u233?nde Deifid a y\u225?njo \u225?r n\u233?ngangoy\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?fenjo t\u225?ik\u233?r atnogh sifayat.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 25
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Samuelene k\u233?rm\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Y\u233?nam\u233? Samuel k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n, a m\u233?inyotio Israil \u225?r namnendam y\u225?ne mban ram\u233?gh\u233?t, Y\u233?mofem yiy\u225?totam\u233?nd y\u225?njo m\u233?ngo k\u233?t\u233? Rama.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Nabal\u233?m n\u233?kwaf\u233? y\u233?fghetam Deifid F\u233?yo
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 F\u233?yo Deifid nimndai k\u233?t\u225?n fanfne yuwot Maon\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
K\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n wemar \u225?r k\u233?tamam\u233?n Maon endene rokar tamor y\u233?n\u233? tesen kaka Karmel yu. Y\u225?ne tamorw\u233?n 3,000 sif a 1,000 gout a sifafen s\u237?f ruf\u233?gh efogh nawerai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?roene y\u233?tkw\u233?n t\u233?morw\u233?n Nabal, a y\u225?ne amaf, Abigail, t\u233?morw\u233?n yaufi a m\u233? y\u225?njo m\u233?ndero m\u233?inyotio yam tawafrotau.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Njam Deifid n\u225?y\u225?rai nden\u233? Nabal\u233?m sifafene s\u237?f tanfetau, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
y\u233?mo engwafaretam 1o y\u225?njom\u233?n tot\u233?r \u225?r k\u233?t\u225?n Karmel yu y\u233?n\u233? siaf\u233? y\u225?yot Nabal! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
"Krufr\u225?t a tomb\u233? gh\u233?rs\u233? feyot, fene m\u233?rnat a m\u233?inyotio fene n\u233?m\u233? em! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Ta t\u233? wafrongi nden\u233? y\u233?m sif s\u237?f ruf\u233?gh efogh. Njamandio fene sif wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r em t\u233?fefaf Karmel yu kaka, y\u233?ndfem yau tawas\u233?mbotam f\u225?, a n\u233?m\u233? yau tawarsat oroe y\u233?fene. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Emota fenjo \u225?r, a y\u233?mofem so k\u233?maufrongi y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m efalo. F\u233?yo f\u233?m so n\u233?m gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? t\u233?fefaf, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd t\u225?f fifi t\u233? t\u233?n\u233?m t\u233?m\u233?nd fifiyan? So mban\u233? ewafte \u225?mb fene rokar m\u233?t\u233? em fene ngangayan t\u233?feyot a fene f\u250?tare Deifide? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Deifidene tot\u233?r ambumm\u233?n \u225?rom yaramai y\u233?n\u233? si y\u225? Nabal Deifidene y\u233?tkw\u233?nan, a f\u225? kawanjetaw\u233?t uwangogh siyot.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Nabal\u233?m yanangotai tot\u233?r \u225?r, "Efe y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r Deifid y\u233?m? Y\u233?n\u233? Jesene ambum ndernaye nemne f\u225? efe y\u233?m? Y\u233?na em t\u225?rf\u225?raf\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r y\u233?n\u233? efghon efe k\u233?rsaw\u233?t y\u233?fenjo ndimbalaf\u233? tamb\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
So y\u233?ndon f\u233?yotaro tangwawanan tane f\u233?skaf flaw\u233? a tane nu a tane w\u233?r\u225?r fenj\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?ndon \u225?rk\u233? tanfetan tane sif s\u237?f ruf\u233?gh \u225?rfet a tawaraman y\u233?fe n\u225?kofnar m\u233?rnat mafina y\u233?n\u233?m \u225?rk\u233?m\u233? enmorm\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
F\u233?yo Deifidene tot\u233?r ambumm\u233?n \u225?r nangoy\u233?ng a yaufroi y\u225? n\u233?m\u233? Nabal t\u233? korayau y\u225?faf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
"Taw\u225?nango f\u233?fenjo witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? naif\u233?!" Deifidene uwangogh y\u233?morm\u233?n t\u225?fandio y\u233?mo y\u225?njoyo ewerai. F\u233?yo 400 \u225?r nufngoy\u233?nd \u225?ligh Deifidf\u233?, a 200 m\u233? emorang\u233?rm\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t tawarendaw\u233?t \u225?mb rokar.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
W\u233?nde, \u225?mb Nabalene \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r y\u233?ngmorm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n Abigail a taufrong\u233? amafoe, "Deifid\u233?m tanwafarete ghan t\u233?fn\u225?r k\u233?tam\u233? fanfne yuta m\u233?n\u225?t so tasnetau t\u233?fene ndimbal, w\u233?nde f\u225? nawambetam ewasalitam f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r t\u233? tam mer t\u233?fefaf, a y\u233?nd yau t\u233?nmas\u233?rmbotat y\u233?mofem a t\u233?n\u233?kmetat t\u233?kratan. N\u233?m\u233? \u225?mb yau oroe tarsat t\u233?feta m\u233?inyotio efogh y\u233?ndf\u233? st\u233?n\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Mbark\u225?nde, efogh a s\u233?mb\u225?r f\u225? ndenanit tam mbakw t\u233?fe wambgh\u233?t a sif k\u233?s em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
F\u233?m so f\u233?t\u233? mat em y\u233?n\u233? a kor yasufetati n\u233?m\u233? so yafrotati, m\u233?nam\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? so y\u233?m k\u233?rt\u233? yam t\u233?fene ndimbaloefaf a m\u233?inyotio y\u225?ne m\u233?r\u233?n. F\u225? siy\u233?m m\u225?m\u233? n\u233?kwro nden\u233? \u225?rk\u233? \u225?rom yau so t\u233?mndang\u233? f\u225?!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
F\u233?yo Abigail w\u233?keye kufrotau a ewanai 200 f\u233?skaf flaw\u233? sut a s\u243?mbio nu s\u233?fkw\u233?n wainaf\u233? a faif f\u233?sfaf kun mbwe a 100 s\u233?fe njamke a 200 figm\u233?n noma, ndonkiefaf tafyotaw\u233?t y\u233?n\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
A norayai y\u225?njo \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?roefaf, "N\u233?ng\u233?m frondeyo, y\u233?ndo so ng\u233?maiton tekofnar." W\u233?nde y\u233?mo yau yaufro y\u225?njar\u233? Nabal n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mo tafrotau.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Njam amaf t\u233?nmorw\u233?n k\u233?n\u233?sau y\u225?njo ndonki k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?n\u233? mband tunakfot rafen, k\u233?t\u233? tamorw\u233?n Deifid a y\u225?ne \u225?r ghak\u233?rro tanmorw\u233?n y\u225? tamb\u233?n, a y\u233?mo efangoi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Deifid m\u233? korayau, "T\u225?rf\u225?r yam t\u233? ewafrotam\u233?nd y\u225?ut\u225?nam\u233?nd f\u225?, y\u233?ndfem tawarawenaw\u233?m y\u225?ne sif fanfne yuwon, a y\u225?ne n\u233?m tamorw\u233?n yau nolinday\u233?nd o oroe enay\u233?nd. W\u233?nde y\u233?mo yaufi wawango ta mer t\u233?fnan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
F\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam kw\u233?smang\u233? y\u233?nd k\u233?rotio t\u225?f y\u225?ne ambiro \u225?r njam t\u233? gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?m k\u225?ye y\u225?ne m\u233?ngota!"
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Abigail kasmetai y\u225?yot Nabal
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Njam Abigail\u233?m yinjoi Deifid, f\u225? w\u233?keye new\u233?ry\u233?nd y\u225?njo ndonkita a y\u225?wefnoi yuwon y\u225?yot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Amaf nuyai y\u225?ne kafkafot a norayai, "Y\u233?ndo yanan m\u233?inyotio t\u233?f\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?rtayan, tane Yur\u233?, gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? n\u225?y\u225?reta y\u233?nan n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?nd s\u225?i korayang\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m Nabal siy\u233?m yaufi a n\u233?kw k\u233?r ro \u225?r, gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? yau t\u225?f y\u233?rareta f\u225?. F\u225? siy\u233?m uny\u233?ghro mato y\u225?ne y\u233?tkw\u233?n nden\u225?ye f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?m. W\u233?nde yau t\u225?f tuyafo tot\u233?r ambum f\u233?mo efe tengwafarete.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
S\u233?nonjo. tane Yur\u233?, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Yur\u233? k\u233?s n\u225?k t\u233? a f\u233?m f\u233?moyo k\u233?s gh\u233?rs\u233? n\u233?m k\u233?tam\u233? Yuram k\u233?s k\u233?mambete k\u233?tam\u233? \u225?r ngita a fai wangogh\u233?t fene ngangayan s\u225?i y\u233?m, so em m\u233?inyotio fene m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r a f\u225? emofem s\u225?i n\u233?mas\u233?rmbotat f\u233?m so tawafalngong\u233? nden\u233? Nabal k\u233?s. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
A y\u233?na y\u233?m t\u233? n\u233?nufar nden\u233? y\u233?nd, fene \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r t\u233? enmanan fefaf a fene tot\u233?r ambum. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? kwawai tane njam y\u233?ndon t\u233? k\u233?rt\u233? k\u233?mawafrotan \u225?mb ende. Yuram so fai n\u233?mafrote f\u233?m m\u233?naye tuot lim\u225?ng\u233?gh yaman, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m n\u225?sm\u233?te Yurane \u225?sm\u233?gh. A f\u233?mo yau m\u225?m\u225?fi yaufrotam fene m\u233?inyotio gh\u233?rsayan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
"Ndemam\u233?n njam n\u233?mifnat y\u233?mofem emofem n\u233?ronjat f\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t sia n\u233?sm\u233?tat k\u233?rotio. Fene gh\u233?rs\u233? siy\u233?m wamb\u233?ghan y\u233?m merro fene Yur\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf, n\u233?nau y\u225?ne mani nj\u233?nan! W\u233?nde fene m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?rafene gh\u233?rs\u233? so n\u233?ngawaindat ndenanit sli\u324? w\u237?me y\u233?nau englaitat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Njam Yuram t\u233? yafrota m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?mo n\u233?m\u233? uny\u233?ghofnar si norayai a t\u233? niy\u225?toi Israil \u225?rfene lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? yam yau so y\u233?fune k\u233?rt\u233? o tikfan ew\u233?rsogh tane Yurai, y\u233?nayaf\u233? f\u233?r\u233?k er\u233?gh t\u233?fnofnar a y\u233?nayan tane Yuram fai tanang\u233? y\u233?monyo. Njam Yuraf\u233? so ere mer awarn\u233?ghan tane yuraf\u233?, f\u233?yo yafarota fenjo \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
Deifid\u233?m yawangoi Abigaile, "\u193?uw\u233?gh Yurai, Israil \u225?rfene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, emo t\u233? k\u233?nafarete f\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? efogh m\u233?n\u225?t ta fangogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
K\u225?njo Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne fene mer mwigham\u233?n! Freng\u233?gh fe m\u233?nam\u233?n wanjar y\u233?nd k\u233?r ngita a k\u233?tam\u233? y\u233?ndonyo s\u225?i fai wangoi tafrotaw\u233?n tanjo ngangaye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Y\u233?nd sote norayan Yurane k\u233?nj\u250?n Israil \u225?rfene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, emo t\u233? kwambete y\u233?nd s\u225?i k\u233?mas\u233?rmbotaw\u233?m f\u233?m, t\u225?f f\u233?m yau njam w\u233?keye kufrotau ta fangogh\u233?t, yau \u225?mb Nabalene \u225?r so kunjarngai k\u225?ye akwan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
F\u233?yo Deifid\u233?m yakawai amafoene ngangata n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mo t\u233? y\u233?nmarsam y\u225? a y\u233?mndai amaf, k\u233?ng\u233?m a ngarmbo fenjo m\u233?ngon \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233?, k\u233?nreta, y\u233?ndo t\u233? k\u233?ny\u225?retan f\u233?m a tafrotan fene m\u233?nde.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
Njam Abigail nufary\u233?ng m\u233?ngotuot, y\u233?mo yinjoi nden\u233? Nabal\u233?m tafrotau ndimbal t\u233?m\u233?nd a ndenanit k\u225?usenaw\u233?t warsagh \u225?r kar t\u233?morw\u233?n. F\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n minde w\u233?ri, f\u233?yo m\u233?rsom yau yaufroi y\u225? \u225?mb m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?ne afangogh Deifidf\u233? k\u233?t\u225?notio \u225?mb efogh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
Akwan t\u225?f Nabal njam w\u233?riofnar t\u233?morw\u233?n, y\u225?ne amafom yaufroi n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? nufrotam. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan fifi y\u233?ramngotam, a f\u225? talimnjong\u233?rw\u233?n njang\u233?n y\u225?njo k\u233?m\u233?gh sifayan w\u237?mnit. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
K\u233?t\u225?n 10 efogh kw\u233?f soram\u233?, Yuram y\u233?smai f\u225?, a k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n.
