Y\u233?nam\u233? Filistain \u225?r ngiot ewanetay\u233?nd Israil \u225?r, a Israil \u225?r ghak\u233?r m\u233?r\u233?n nawatembay\u233?nd y\u233?feta t\u225?rf\u225?r t\u233?nyaw\u233?t mband tunak\u233?f Giboa ewar\u233?ghta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Filistain \u225?r\u233?m ewembay\u233?nd Sol a y\u225?ne ghak\u233?r ambum, a y\u233?mofem esmay\u233?nd k\u233?rotio y\u225?ne nambio ambum-Jonatan, Abinadab, a Malkisua. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
\u193?sm\u233?gh namndai k\u233?rtaye Soleta, a namb wer\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?ram y\u233?smay\u233?nd f\u225?, a m\u225?m\u233?gh\u233?raye kal y\u225?frotam\u233?nd m\u233?nayam namb wer\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?ram.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
F\u233?yo Sol norayai y\u225?njo \u225?sm\u233?gh wamb\u233?gh \u225?roefaf, "T\u233?nman fene witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? naif\u233? a kw\u233?kuin y\u233?naye, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?ghat men w\u225?wefnogh \u225?r\u233?m m\u233?t\u233? t\u225?f w\u233?kuindat a ewafrotat mbor tafaf." W\u233?nde y\u225?ne \u225?sm\u233?gh wamb\u233?gh \u225?rom yau yafrotam, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? minde f\u233?rf\u233?r t\u233?morw\u233?n. F\u233?yo Sol\u233?m yanai y\u225?ne witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? naif\u233? a nuyai k\u233?t\u225?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Njam y\u225?ne \u225?sm\u233?gh wamb\u233?gh \u225?r yinjoi nden\u233? Sol k\u233?r t\u233? y\u233?morm\u233?n, f\u225? w\u233?i nden\u225?yo nuyai y\u225?njo witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? naifafaf nuyai a k\u233?r erm\u233?n y\u233?maf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u233?yo Sol k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n y\u233?maf\u233? y\u225?njo nambio ambumaf\u233?, y\u225?ne m\u233?k \u225?sm\u233?gh wamb\u233?gh \u225?rf\u233?, a y\u225?ne \u225?rf\u233? m\u233?inyotio m\u233?rne.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Njam Israil \u225?r ghak\u233?r m\u233?rnam efe tamorw\u233?m witm\u233? mband ewor\u233?gh kar\u233?f, y\u233?maf\u233? emof\u233? Joden frondeta tamorw\u233?n, ewinjoy\u233?nd Israil \u225?r ghak\u233?r m\u233?r\u233?n t\u233? nawatembay\u233?nd a nden\u233? Sol a y\u225?ne ambum k\u233?r t\u233? emorm\u233?n, y\u233?mofem efrangoy\u233?nd tesen k\u233?rsaw\u233?t. F\u233?yo Filistain \u225?r enmorm\u233?n a k\u233?t\u233? t\u225?kmang\u233?rw\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?morm\u233?n \u225?mb y\u233?namayo efghon njam Filistain enmorm\u233?n rokar fitrargh\u233?t y\u233?fefaf efe k\u233?rotio esmetam\u233?nd, a y\u233?mofem ewinjoy\u233?nd Sol a y\u225?ne nambio ambum nuyay\u233?nd k\u233?t\u233? mband tunak\u233?ffaf Gilboa. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Y\u233?mofem y\u233?nfay\u233?nd yame s\u233?nko a yafit\u233?rnam\u233?nd y\u225?ne \u225?sm\u233?gh rokar, a engwatembay\u233?nd y\u233?nam\u233? Filistain yuwom\u233?, m\u233?n\u225?t so t\u233?ng\u233?rsaw\u233?t mer si k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?fene mewang w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngota k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?rfefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Y\u233?mofem ekmay\u233?nd y\u225?ne \u225?sm\u233?gh rokar y\u233?n\u233? w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngon Astarot a y\u233?mofem y\u233?frendam\u233?n y\u225?ne fifi k\u233?t\u225?n Bet-san mbakwfaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
W\u233?nde njam Jabes-giliad \u225?r n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd n\u233?m\u233? Filistain \u225?r\u233?m yafrotam\u233?nd y\u225?faf Solefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
M\u233?inyotio y\u233?fene m\u233?k s\u233?nko \u225?r nuwanoy\u233?nd s\u233?mb\u225?ran k\u233?t\u225?n Bet-san a y\u233?ngwanay\u233?nd Solene fifi a y\u225?ne ambum k\u233?tam\u233? mbakwta. Y\u233?mofem en\u233?rsam\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n Jabes, \u225?nde y\u233?mofem ewaray\u233?nd fifi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
