Solene ambum Jonatanene t\u233?morw\u233?n ambum y\u233?tkw\u233?n M\u233?fiboset efe tosayan njang\u233?n namndai f\u225? t\u225?f t\u233?morw\u233?n 5 y\u250?nj\u233?f njam si y\u233?nmorm\u233?n k\u233?tam\u233? Jejrieleta nden\u233? Sol a Jonatan t\u233? t\u225?smet k\u233?rotio m\u233?kan. Njam ambum manjar\u233?gh amofom si n\u225?y\u225?rai, y\u233?mo y\u233?kafai a nawatembai. W\u233?nde w\u233?keye njam ngurotau, y\u233?mo y\u233?ngwitam, a f\u225? namndai njang\u233?n.
