A w\u233?ikor Deifid\u233?m y\u233?motai Yur\u233? n\u233?m\u233? so yafrotan. Yuram yawangoi, "Yau t\u225?f tainda f\u225? \u225?mb r\u233?rero. W\u233?nde, tawarendangi s\u233?mta a taindangi kaka y\u233?n\u233? fofla w\u233?nfafm\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Njam f\u233?mofem n\u225?y\u225?retati ke ndenanit foflena kafkaf y\u233?nau eitat y\u233?n\u233? fofla w\u233?n tuk\u233?n, kor aem! Y\u233?n\u233? so y\u233?m waufar\u233?gh nden\u233? Yur\u233? nimnde fronde f\u233?ta m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tasmang\u233? Filistain fiyar\u233?." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
F\u233?yo Deifid yafrotam y\u233?n\u233? n\u233?mat Yuram yafaretai, a y\u233?mo tasmetau Filistain \u225?r m\u233?inyotio k\u233?tam\u233? Gibeon k\u233?t\u225?notio Gejer.
