F\u233?yo Deifid\u233?m w\u233?ikor eumendam mer fiyar\u233? m\u233?r\u233?n Israil k\u233?nj\u250?n, 30,000 m\u233?inyotio. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Y\u233?mo elimndam f\u225? k\u233?t\u225?n Baalefaf Judam\u233?n t\u233?morw\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t so t\u233?nmangotaw\u233?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?mofem y\u233?fayoy\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u225?k boks tot\u233?r r\u233?sagh rokar a y\u233?nmanay\u233?nd y\u233?nd k\u233?tam\u233? Abinadabene m\u233?ngota, '\u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n mband tunakfan, Ujia a Aio, Abinadabene ambum, tambetaw\u233?t r\u233?sagh rokar k\u233?t\u225?notio kor y\u233?frangoi m\u233?ngo, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
tarsaw\u233?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u225?k boks. Aio frondeyo tiyotau n\u225?k boksta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Deifid a m\u233?inyotio Israil \u225?r t\u225?rf\u225?r tafrotaw\u233?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene r\u233?re, taufanaw\u233?t wagh a ngambnaw\u233?t f\u233?nataf\u233?nat\u233? kembnem\u233?n wagh rokare-laire, af, tambarine, kastanet, a simbal.
