W\u233?nde njam f\u225? nufary\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n n\u225?koene wagh sifayafaf kau n\u233?us\u233?mbotam a Ujam engwatembai y\u225?njo ng\u225?ng\u233? a y\u233?kmbo, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u225?k boks. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u233?kw nokayoi y\u225?faf Uja a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?smai f\u225? k\u233?rotio y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan. F\u233?yo Uja k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? t\u233?ndon Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u225?k boksfaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Deifid n\u233?kwam y\u225?indai m\u233?nam\u233?n Yurane n\u233?kwam t\u233? yanai Uja. Y\u233?mo y\u233?n\u233? sifayai y\u233?tkw\u233?n yaramai Ferej-Uja(y\u225?ne fifi siy\u233?m yanai n\u233?kwam f\u225? Uja), s\u233?nonjo ju m\u233? yanmotat.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Deifid y\u233?nam\u233? f\u233?rf\u233?ram yifoi Yurafaf, a f\u225? namotai, "Ndern\u225?ye so y\u233?ndo Yurane n\u225?k boks tane k\u233?nj\u250?t wanjeng\u233?gh\u233?t?" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?yo Deifid\u233?m mwigh\u233? y\u233?faronam yau s\u225?i tit\u233?rmbongai Yurane n\u225?k boks k\u233?t\u225?n Deifidene ndimbal tesenfaf, w\u233?nde y\u233?mo y\u233?ng\u233?rsam k\u233?t\u225?n Obed-edomene m\u233?ngot t\u233?morw\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? yum\u233?n Gat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Yurane n\u225?k boks y\u233?kmang\u233?rm\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? Obed-edomene m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?n k\u233?t\u225?n 3 gh\u233?rare, a Yuram y\u233?frendai Obed-Edom a y\u225?ne m\u233?inyotio m\u233?r\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
F\u233?yo warsagh \u225?r Deifide yaufroy\u233?nd, "Yuram t\u233? efrenda Obed-edomene m\u233?r\u233?n a m\u233?inyotio rokar y\u225?ne n\u233?m\u233? em m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u225?k boksm\u233?n." F\u233?yo Deifid k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?ngmorm\u233?n a y\u233?nmorm\u233?n a y\u233?nmanai Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u225?k boks k\u233?tam\u233? Obed-edomene m\u233?ngota k\u233?t\u225?n Deifidene ndimbal tesenfaf ndimbal wafyauaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?roe soram\u233? emo t\u233?rsau Yurane n\u225?k boks t\u233? engyai kafkaf 6 mbinotm\u233?, Deifid\u233?m gh\u233?ng\u233?n yafrotam kau a nj\u233?maro sif. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
A Deifid erm\u225?ng\u233?gh nufngoi Yurane r\u233?re m\u233?naye m\u233?inyotio muyaye tawong\u233?rw\u233?n gh\u233?ng\u233?n warogh \u225?rfene s\u225?l\u225?me. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?yo Deifid a m\u233?inyotio Israil \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?n\u233?rsam\u233?nd Yurane n\u225?k boks \u225?uw\u233?gh keyaf\u233? a tanwaufetaw\u233?t sif t\u225?rt\u225?r.
