W\u233?nde njam Yurane n\u225?k boks n\u233?nyawai Deifidene ndimbal tesen, Mikal, Solene m\u233?r\u233?s, k\u233?nretau k\u233?tam\u233? m\u233?ngo tuk f\u233?nat\u233?, Njam y\u233?mo yinjoi warsagh \u225?r Deifid ngatnau a nger\u233?mndau Yurane r\u233?re. F\u225? m\u233?ndm\u233?nd t\u233?morw\u233?n y\u225?faf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Y\u233?mofem y\u233?n\u233?rsam\u233?nd Yurane n\u225?k boks y\u233?kmany\u233?nd y\u225?njo sifayan \u225?mb farai m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?n \u225?rk\u233?m\u233? Deifid\u233?m t\u233? y\u233?frendam y\u233?nat. A Deifid\u233?m gh\u233?ng\u233?n warsagh ram\u233?ghyam a krufrat \u225?mnjogh gh\u233?ng\u233?n yafrotam Yurai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Njam y\u233?mo yifoi y\u225?njo gh\u233?ng\u233?n, Deifid\u233?m efrendai \u225?r njafarm\u233?n fiyarafene Yurane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mo tawarametau m\u233?inyotio Israilm\u233?n \u225?r ghak\u233?rat a amafat \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?n flaw\u233?, a noma a \u225?mb s\u233?f t\u225?rf\u225?r noma, F\u233?yo m\u233?inyotio \u225?r kangotaw\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?fenjo m\u233?ngot.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Njam Deifid nangotam m\u233?ngot m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tafrendangai y\u225?njo m\u233?r\u233?n, Mikal, Solene m\u233?r\u233?s, n\u233?ntory\u233?ng a y\u233?nmanfetati f\u225?, a n\u233?ngorayai \u225?uw\u233?ghofnar si, "Ndern\u225?ye \u225?uw\u233?ghofnar Israilm\u233?n warsagh \u225?r n\u233?rete s\u233?nonjo, w\u225?iw\u225?iyaf\u233? nauyafote y\u225?njo w\u225?s\u225?fogh m\u233?r\u233?safefaf ndenanit ong\u233?n \u225?rom y\u233?nau y\u233?ngafrote yam!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Deifid\u233?m y\u233?mndai Mikal, "Y\u233?nd keremndaw\u233?n Yurane r\u233?re, emo w\u233?kafai y\u233?nd y\u233?fene tuk\u233?n fene feraf\u233? a y\u225?ne m\u233?r\u233?n! Y\u233?mo uyafoi y\u233?nd s\u225?i w\u233?m lim\u225?n\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r Israil\u233?t, Yurane \u225?r\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
N\u233?m\u233?w\u233?t, a y\u233?nd m\u233?nde f\u233?t\u233? w\u233?m s\u225?i n\u233?retan mindeye ong\u233?n \u225?r y\u233?nata, yuwan so nafandan tane gh\u233?kfan! W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? 7 w\u225?s\u225?fogh m\u233?r\u233?sm\u233?r\u233?s f\u233?mo \u225?rk\u233? emnd\u233? so f\u225? nemnat y\u233?nd \u225?uw\u233?ghofnar t\u233? namndan!" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
F\u233?yo Mikal Solene m\u233?r\u233?s, y\u233?morang\u233?rm\u233?n ambumofnar y\u225?ne m\u233?inyotio gh\u233?rsayan.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 7
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yurane uny\u233?ghofnar \u193?rny\u233?gh si y\u225?faf Deifid
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Njam warsagh \u225?r Deifid kor n\u225?mnjoi y\u225?njo utman\u233?gh sifayan a Yuram t\u233? yaramai enagh k\u233?tam\u233? m\u233?inyotio m\u233?k \u225?rfene wareng\u233?ghta, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
warsagh \u225?rom y\u233?faretai Natan Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r, "K\u233?reta, Deifid norayai, "Y\u233?nd w\u233?mor mer sedar sariaf\u233? utman\u233?gh m\u233?ngon, w\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u225?k boks k\u233?s y\u233?m k\u233?t\u233? farai m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?n!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Natan yawangoi warsagh \u225?roe, "T\u233?ngwafngo y\u233?n\u233? n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? y\u233?m fene mwighayan, m\u233?nam\u233?n Yur\u233? siy\u233?m fefaf y\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? s\u233?mb\u225?ranyo Yuram y\u233?mndai Natan,
\par\pard\plain \s74\ql\fi0\lin360\rin360\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
"Keng\u233?m t\u233?mnd\u233? tane w\u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?roe Deifid, y\u233?n\u233? Yuram y\u233?ny\u225?to. F\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?t\u233? n\u233?m siya m\u233?ngo y\u233?rameta tayot \u225?nde so w\u233?mor? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u233?nd \u225?nde yau kw\u233?mor m\u233?ngon, k\u233?t\u225?mayo y\u233?n\u233? kw\u233?f y\u233?ndon sen\u233?utory\u233?n Israil \u225?r k\u233?tam\u233? Ijif y\u233?nanotio s\u233?nonjo kw\u233?f. Y\u233?nd t\u250?m\u233?n kimndan k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mb sifay\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mb sifay\u233? m\u233?nayaf\u233? farai m\u233?ngoyaf\u233? a ndimbal farai m\u233?ngo tane enyaughaghm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
W\u233?nde, yau k\u233?rt\u233? y\u233?m \u225?rkam\u233? y\u233?nd kw\u233?yotau Israil \u225?rf\u233? y\u233?nd yau \u225?nde \u225?mbirotaro n\u225?watarnay\u233?n Israil m\u233?rnafene lim\u225?n\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?rafefaf, sif wanjeng\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r tane \u225?r Israilm\u233?n. Y\u233?ndo yau \u225?mb emotay\u233?n f\u225?, "N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?mofem yau t\u233?rametati sariaf\u233? sedar m\u233?ngo?"
\par\pard\plain \s69\ql\fi180\lin360\rin360\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
"S\u233?nonjo kuwano a t\u233?mnd\u233? tane w\u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r Deifid, Y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?y\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? Yurane njafarm\u233?n fiyaram t\u233? y\u233?ny\u225?tongi. Y\u233?ndo n\u233?manay\u233?n y\u233?nam\u233? t\u250?m\u233?n sif tawanjetau yus n\u233?neyan a n\u233?kafay\u233?n fem m\u233?n\u225?t namndai Israil \u225?rfene lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Y\u233?nd t\u233? f\u233?maf\u233? t\u233?nre \u225?rkam\u233? f\u233?m k\u233?nyota, a y\u233?ndo t\u233? tangwironan m\u233?inyotio fene m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r fene gh\u233?k\u233?f r\u233?re. S\u233?nonjo y\u233?ndon so tiy\u225?ton fene y\u233?tkw\u233?n marat mindefifi efe \u225?mb yau nden\u233? y\u233?morang\u233?rm\u233?n y\u233?na mbandan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?ndon so tawaraman m\u233?ngotuot mband k\u233?t\u225?n tane \u225?r\u233?t Israil, eitan k\u233?t\u233? wamb\u233?gh sifayafaf \u225?nde yau so eus\u233?rmbotat. Yaufiyam k\u233?r ro marat yu k\u233?s em yau so esenat f\u225? nden\u233? ndernaye tawafrotaw\u233?t t\u225?nd\u225?i, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
N\u233?narnyai k\u233?tam\u233? y\u233?n\u233? efoghta y\u233?ndo \u225?nde ekafetam\u233?n mogh t\u233?fn\u225?r m\u233?n\u225?t so talimndaw\u233?t tane \u225?r Israilm\u233?n. F\u233?yo y\u233?ndo so tawaraman enagh f\u233?fe m\u233?inyotio f\u233?fene m\u233?k \u225?rfeta.
\par\pard\plain \s69\ql\fi180\lin360\rin360\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "W\u233?i m\u233? kor, Yuram t\u233? yiy\u225?toi nden\u233? y\u233?mo so y\u233?ramete m\u233?ngo f\u233?fe-a y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?r\u233?nm\u233?n so em warsagh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Njam f\u233?m kor em a ey\u225?totat f\u233?fene \u225?kif\u233?, y\u233?ndon so w\u233?i takayon \u225?mb f\u233?fenem\u233?n \u225?kim\u233?n f\u233?fenjoyo ambum, a y\u233?ndon so tiy\u225?ton y\u225?ne lim\u225?n\u233?gh muyaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u225? Y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?y\u233?m emo so y\u233?ramete m\u233?ngo w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo-tane y\u233?tkw\u233?not. A y\u233?ndon tanjaren y\u225?ne ambino lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? tuot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?nd so w\u233?m y\u225?ne af\u233?, a f\u225? so y\u233?m tane ambum, njam y\u233?mo yaufiyam yafrota, y\u233?ndo so y\u233?rermetan f\u225? tot t\u233?f\u233?n yakaye, nden\u233?yame y\u225?refam kar y\u225?frote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
W\u233?nde tane m\u233?nde yau so t\u233?ngwanan y\u225? tamb\u233?n nden\u233? Soleta k\u233?s y\u233?nmanay\u233?n, efe y\u233?ndon t\u233? yimnday\u233?n f\u233?fene r\u233?re. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u233?fene m\u233?ngo a f\u233?fene warsagh \u225?r lim\u225?n\u233?gh so nusamngote tane s\u225?f r\u233?re m\u233?inyotio t\u250?m\u233?n efogh, a f\u233?fene lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? so wanjar\u233?ghan y\u233?m tuot."
