\par\pard\plain \s74\ql\fi0\lin360\rin360\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "Efe y\u233?nd w\u233?m, waft\u233? k\u233?r ro Yur\u233?, a n\u233?m\u233? em tane m\u233?r\u233?n, nden\u233? f\u233?mo t\u233? kw\u233?n\u233?rse nden\u233? yu nayu? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
F\u233?yo s\u233?nonjo, waft\u233? k\u233?r ro Yur\u233?, farut m\u233?inyotio yaman, f\u233?m t\u233? koray\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n s\u225?i tawaram fene w\u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r\u233?t tuot warsagh \u225?r lim\u225?n\u233?gh waft\u233?! F\u233?mo f\u233?t\u233? yafrote m\u233?inyotio \u225?rfefaf nden\u233? endero, o waft\u233? k\u233?r ro Yur\u233??
\par\pard\plain \s69\ql\fi180\lin360\rin360\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
"N\u233?mat kor so n\u233?norayan fefaf? f\u233?m mat n\u233?m ndernaye fene w\u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r y\u233?m, waft\u233? k\u233?r ro Yur\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n fene uny\u233?ghofnar sim\u233?n a fene m\u233?ndeyam\u233?, f\u233?mo t\u233? tawafrote m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? ndimbal yam a t\u233? mat t\u225?y\u225?tote fene w\u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s69\ql\fi180\lin360\rin360\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
"Nder\u233? ndimbal f\u233?m n\u233?m, o waft\u233? k\u233?r ro Yur\u233?! Y\u233?na yau y\u233?m \u225?mb \u225?r nden\u233? f\u233?m s\u233?n\u233?m, Y\u233?nd yau n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?m \u225?mb Ng\u225?nj\u225?nenem\u233?n m\u233? fenem\u233?nro. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
N\u233?m\u233? \u225?mb ndimbal yu y\u233?n\u233? mbandan t\u233? em nden\u233? fene \u225?r Israil sem? \u193?rk\u233? ndimbal yu em, o Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, t\u233? f\u233?mo ewanjar k\u233?tam\u233? faiofnar \u225?s\u225?foghta m\u233?nd s\u225?i em fene \u225?r? F\u233?mon t\u233? yafrotam ndimbal y\u233?tkw\u233?n fendio njam f\u233?mo ewanjary\u233?ng fene \u225?r k\u233?tam\u233? Ijif. F\u233?mo matot s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam tawafrotau a tangtarnau ndimbal yu a ng\u225?nj\u225?nng\u225?nj\u225?n \u225?rk\u233? tawakayong\u233?rw\u233?n y\u233?fenjo endm\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
F\u233?mo ewafrotam fenjofifi Israil \u225?r tuot, a f\u233?m, O Yur\u233?, n\u233?namndai y\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n.
\par\pard\plain \s69\ql\fi180\lin360\rin360\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
"A s\u233?nonjo, o Yur\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, y\u233?nd w\u233?m fene w\u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, ewafrota nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u233?m t\u233? norayai uny\u233?ghofnar si m\u233?nam\u233?n tanem\u233?n a tane m\u233?r\u233?n. Tiy\u225?to so y\u233?m uny\u233?ghofnar si \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? so nakete tuot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
A so fene y\u233?tkw\u233?n yut\u233?mndat tuot m\u233?n\u225?t m\u233?inyotio \u225?r so norayat, njafarm\u233?n fiyarafene Yur\u233? siy\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n y\u233?m Israil \u225?r\u233?t!. A so fene \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?roene Deifidene m\u233?ngo m\u233? y\u233?ng\u233?m fene r\u233?re tuot.
\par\pard\plain \s69\ql\fi180\lin360\rin360\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
O njafarm\u233?n fiyarafene Yur\u233?, Israil \u225?rfene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n y\u233?nd t\u233? marataye kw\u233?m f\u233?yotaroe m\u233?n\u225?t korayaw\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf oray\u233?gh fefaf m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mo t\u233? saf\u233?n takmetau m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n fene \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r, korayau, 'Y\u233?ndo so y\u233?rametan m\u233?ngo feyot \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? so m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? n\u233?f\u233?rmete warsagh \u225?r lim\u225?n\u233?gh waft\u233?! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, o waft\u233? k\u233?r ro Yur\u233?. Fene si sem efalo, a f\u233?mo t\u233? uny\u233?ghofnar si norayai y\u233?n\u233? yamm\u233?n fene \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?roefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
A s\u233?nonjo, so f\u233?m klisaf\u233? n\u233?m y\u233?nayan m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i freng\u233?gham y\u233?rsa fene \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?roene m\u233?ngo, m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?n\u233? so m\u233? y\u233?ng\u233?m tuot fene r\u233?re. M\u233?nam\u233?n fem t\u233? norayai, a njam f\u233?mo y\u233?ramai freng\u233?gh yam k\u233?t\u225?n fene \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?roefaf, o waft\u233? k\u233?r ro Yur\u233?, y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m tuot akegh freng\u233?gh!"
