F\u233?yo Deifid\u233?m ewafaretam y\u225?faf a y\u233?nmasroy\u233?nd f\u225? k\u233?tam\u233? Makirene m\u233?ngota. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u225?ne y\u233?tkw\u233?n t\u233?morw\u233?n Mefiboset. F\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n Jonatanene ambum a Solene \u225?ki ambum. Njam f\u225? n\u233?naflai k\u233?t\u225?n Deifidefaf, f\u225? n\u225?wefnoi yuwot k\u233?t\u225?n mband ndimbal k\u233?njkam utman\u233?ghaf\u233?. Deifid norayai. \u193?sneghaf\u233?, Mefiboset."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Mefiboset\u233?m yawangoi, "Y\u233?nd w\u233?m fene \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Deifid\u233?m y\u233?mndai, "Yau f\u233?rf\u233?r n\u233?m! Y\u233?nd m\u233?n\u225?t karametan siya tuyafongay\u233?n ram\u233?gh tik\u233?f fefaf m\u233?nam\u233?n tane uny\u233?ghofnar si fene ferafefaf, Jonatan. Y\u233?ndon so k\u233?maraman fe m\u233?inyotio y\u225?nem\u233?n rokar \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? tamorw\u233?n fene fekienem\u233?n Sol, a f\u233?mo so enete y\u233?na y\u233?ndf\u233? warsagh \u225?rfene s\u233?kiyan!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Mefiboset n\u225?wefnoi utman\u233?ghaf\u233? a norayai, "Efe y\u233?m fene \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, nden\u233? f\u233?mo s\u225?i tuyafo nden\u233? ram\u233?gh tik\u233?f y\u233?nau k\u233?rw\u233?n \u225?ghafaf nden\u233? y\u233?nd?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
F\u233?yo warsagh \u225?rom y\u233?mndai Solene \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r Jiba a norayai. Y\u233?ndo t\u233? yaramay\u233?n fene ndimbaloene \u225?ki ambumoe m\u233?inyotio rokar \u225?rk\u233? tamorw\u233?n Solene a y\u225?ne m\u233?rnafene. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?m a fene ambum a fene \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r ndawot yafrotati mband y\u225?yot m\u233?n\u225?t so nafunat njamke y\u233?fe fene ndimbaloene m\u233?rnat. W\u233?nde Mefiboset, fene ndimbaloene \u225?ki ambumom, so enete y\u233?na tane s\u233?kiyan." Jibane tamorw\u233?n 15 ghak\u233?r ambum a 12 \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Jibam yawangoi, "A, tane yur\u233? warsagh \u225?r, y\u233?nd w\u233?m fene \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, a y\u233?ndon so ewafrotan m\u233?inyotio n\u233?mat f\u233?mo t\u233? wafaretai." F\u233?yo y\u233?n\u233? efoghta, Mefiboset\u233?m t\u250?m\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? Deifidene s\u233?kiyan, ndenanit \u225?mb warsagh \u225?roene ambumnit.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Mefibosetene t\u233?morw\u233?n tot\u233?r ambum y\u225?ne y\u233?tkw\u233?n t\u233?morw\u233?n Mika. F\u233?yo efe t\u225?kmang\u233?rw\u233?n y\u225?ne m\u233?ngon Jiba tamorw\u233?n Mefibosetene w\u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
A Mefiboset, efe t\u233?morw\u233?n s\u243?mbio kafkaf m\u225?m\u225?fi t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? Jerusalem\u233?n a tanetau t\u250?m\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? warsagh \u225?roene s\u233?kiyan.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 10
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Deifid\u233?m m\u233?kan ewaindai Amon \u225?r
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
\u193?mb efogh y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233?, warsagh \u225?r Naas Amonm\u233?n k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n, f\u233?yo y\u225?ne ambum Anun n\u233?namndai warsagh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Deifid norayai, "Y\u233?ndon so yuyafotan tik\u233?f y\u225?faf Anun, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u225?ref\u233?, Naas, ndernaye tikfaf\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n tafaf. F\u233?yo Deifid\u233?m engwafaretam mat si \u225?r m\u233?n\u225?t so gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? si taramangay\u233?nd y\u225? Anun m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?refanem\u233?n k\u233?rm\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 W\u233?nde njam Deifidene mat si \u225?r nufary\u233?nd k\u233?t\u233? Amon mbandan, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Amon fiyar\u233? wafar\u233?gh s\u233?nko \u225?r norayay\u233?nd \u225?r y\u233?nan en\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t so yut\u233?mndat fene af\u233?? Yau! Deifid\u233?m enwafaretam f\u225? m\u233?n\u225?t so tiyamndaw\u233?t ndimbal tesen m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? so k\u233?nyawangi a tanangi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
F\u233?yo Anun\u233?m ronjagh ewafngoi Deifidene mat si \u225?rfene f\u233?t s\u237?f mbarmbare tanfetaw\u233?t y\u233?fene s\u225?l\u225?me kw\u233?mb tamb\u233?n a tangwangongay\u233?nd f\u225? k\u233?t\u225?n Deifidefaf w\u225?iw\u225?iaf\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Njam Deifid n\u225?y\u225?rai n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? nufrotam, y\u233?mo \u225?r engwafaretam siaf\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t so tawaufrongay\u233?nd \u225?r, ghak\u233?rat, "Emor k\u233?t\u233? Jeriko k\u233?t\u225?notio f\u233?fene f\u233?t s\u237?f kor nafyanat, a w\u233?i n\u233?nangotati." F\u225? k\u233?njkam w\u225?iw\u225?iam ewifoi m\u233?nam\u233?n ndernaye k\u233?retaw\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Njam Amonm\u233?n \u225?r mat n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd ndernaye minde n\u233?kwaf\u233? y\u233?fetam\u233?nd Deifid. Y\u233?mofem engwafaretam\u233?nd a manie ernay\u233?nd 20,000 Aramm\u233?n kafkafe \u225?ligh t\u233?fn\u225?r fiyar\u233? y\u233?n\u233? mbandta Bet-reob a Joba, 1,000 k\u233?tam\u233? warsagh \u225?roeta Maaka a 12,000 k\u233?tam\u233? Tob mbandm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Njam Deifid n\u225?y\u225?rai y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n, y\u233?ngwafaretam Joab a y\u225?ne fiyar\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?fe \u225?sm\u233?gh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Amonm\u233?n fiyar\u233? n\u233?ntory\u233?nd a n\u233?nimnday\u233?nd \u225?sm\u233?gh\u233?t folenero k\u233?t\u233? ndimbal tesen s\u233?safnefaf, t\u225?f Aramm\u233?n \u225?r k\u233?t\u225?mam\u233?n Joba a Reob a \u225?r ghak\u233?r k\u233?t\u225?mam\u233?n Tob a Maaka \u225?sm\u233?gh\u233?t kafrendaw\u233?t fanfne sifayan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Njam Joab\u233?m ewinjoi nden\u233? \u225?sm\u233?gh\u233?t s\u243?mbio s\u225?f so y\u233?m frondeta a soramata y\u233?mo ekafai \u225?mb sotaf\u233? Israilm\u233?n m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r a ewakayoi y\u225?ne wafregh mbanmbanot m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i k\u225?sm\u233?taw\u233?t Aramm\u233?n \u225?rf\u233? ndau sifayam\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Y\u233?mo efrangoi \u225?mb fiyar\u233? y\u225?n\u233? Abisai y\u225?nng\u233?n wafar\u233?gh mbanmbanan, emo so \u225?sm\u233?gh tafngongai Amonm\u233?n \u225?rfefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Joab\u233?m y\u233?mndai y\u225?nng\u233?n, "Njam Aramm\u233?n \u225?r minde muyaf\u233? tayot en\u233?m t\u225?f ta w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t. A njam Amonm\u233?n fiyar\u233? em minde muyaf\u233? fefaf, y\u233?nd so t\u225?f w\u233?n\u233?m a n\u233?m\u225?ut\u225?nan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Muyaf\u233? ay\u233?m! So n\u225?smetam mer k\u233?r\u225?ye t\u233?fene \u225?r t\u233?fnan a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ndimbal tesenm\u233?n. So Yurane m\u233?nde nufrote."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Njam Joab a y\u225?ne fiyaram \u225?sm\u233?gh engwafngoy\u233?nd, Aram fiyar\u233? w\u233?rse nufngoy\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
A njam Amon fiyaram ewinjoy\u233?nd Aramm\u233?n fiyar\u233? k\u233?rsaw\u233?t f\u225? w\u233?rse nufngoy\u233?nd k\u233?tam\u233? Abisai a nufanam\u233?nd ndimbal tesenfaf. Soram\u233? njam \u225?sm\u233?gh nefoi, Joab kangotau k\u233?t\u225?n Jerusalem\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Aramm\u233?n fiyar\u233? y\u233?nam\u233? mat namnday\u233?nd nden\u233? f\u225? f\u233?yotarofnar tamorw\u233?n Israil fiyarafet. F\u233?yo njam y\u233?mofem m\u233?r\u233?n ewafrotam\u233?nd, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
y\u233?fefaf w\u233?ikor nufnyay\u233?nd Aramm\u233?n fiyar\u233? m\u233?r\u233?n ewafaretai y\u233?mo Adadeja k\u233?tam\u233? Eufrates wanje witm\u233? kar\u233?fta. Y\u233?n\u233? fiyar\u233? m\u233?r\u233?n nufary\u233?nd k\u233?t\u233? Elam Sobakene wafar\u233?gh mbanmbanan, efe t\u233?morw\u233?n Adadejane fiyarafene wafar\u233?gh s\u233?nko \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Njam Deifid n\u225?y\u225?rai n\u233?m\u233? katyanau, y\u233?mo eumendam m\u233?inyotio Israil fiyar\u233?, k\u233?f\u233?rmetaw\u233?t Joden wanje, a elimndam fiyar\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n Elam. Aramm\u233?n fiyaram sifay\u233? ersam\u233?nd y\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?n \u225?sm\u233?gh s\u225?f yafrotam\u233?nd a \u225?sm\u233?gh nufngoy\u233?nd Deifidf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
W\u233?nde w\u233?ikor Aramm\u233?n fiyar\u233? w\u233?rse nufngoy\u233?nd Israil fiyarafeta. Y\u233?n\u233? efghon Deifidene fiyaram esmetam\u233?nd 700 os w\u233?rse t\u233?fn\u225?r a 40,000 kafkafe \u225?ligh t\u233?fn\u225?r fiyar\u233?, y\u233?mafayo Sobak, y\u233?fene fiyarafene wafar\u233?gh s\u233?nko t\u233?fn\u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Njam m\u233?inyotio warsagh \u225?r naufoy\u233?nd y\u233?maf\u233? Adadeja yinjoy\u233?nd nden\u233? t\u233? Israilam y\u225?inday\u233?nd, f\u225? namyoy\u233?nd Israilafefaf a namnday\u233?nd y\u233?feyot. Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233?, Aramm\u233?n \u225?r f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? tamorw\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i taw\u225?ut\u225?naw\u233?t Amonm\u233?n fiyar\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 11
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Deifid a Betsiba
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Y\u250?nj\u233?fan, njam warsagh \u225?r t\u250?m\u233?n t\u225?f tangmorw\u233?n m\u233?kot, Deifid\u233?m engwafaretam Joab a Israil fiyar\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i t\u225?smetaw\u233?t Amon fiyar\u233?. Y\u233?mofem y\u233?nam\u233?nd Amon fiyar\u233? a wan\u233?gh yafngoy\u233?nd ndimbal tesen Raba. W\u233?nde Deifid m\u233? y\u233?morang\u233?rm\u233?n Jerusalem s\u233?mta.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Soram\u233? s\u233?itefifian, soram\u233? y\u225?ne n\u233?ndk\u233?f enagh k\u233?nj\u250?n, Deifid nanoi k\u233?m\u233?gh sifayata a tiyotau utman\u233?gh m\u233?ngo s\u233?msot tuk\u233?n. Njam f\u225? k\u233?retau k\u233?t\u225?n ndimbal tesenfaf, y\u233?mo yinjoi sariaf\u233? amaf anu kumbnau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?mo y\u233?ngwafaretam \u225?mb \u225?r kor s\u225?i tinjongai efe temorw\u233?n, a y\u225? yafroi, "F\u225? y\u233?m Batsiba, Eliamene m\u233?r\u233?s a Uriane amaf Itaitm\u233?n \u225?roene." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
F\u233?yo Deifid\u233?m engwafaretam siaf\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i t\u233?nmasrongay\u233?nd Batsiba a njam f\u225? y\u233?nmorm\u233?n y\u233?nan utman\u233?gh m\u233?ngot, Deifid\u233?f ekmarm\u233?n y\u233?maf\u233?. Betsiba gh\u233?rare enjneta mer namndai. F\u233?yo n\u233?ngangotam m\u233?ngot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Soram\u233? t\u225?f Batsiba njam nawinjoi nden\u233? f\u225? suaf\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n, y\u233?mo y\u233?ngwawatembai si Deifide, norayai, "Y\u233?nd w\u233?m suaf\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u233?yo Deifid\u233?m si y\u233?ngwatembai y\u225? Joabe: "T\u233?nmafareta tafaf Uria Itait \u225?r." F\u233?yo Joab\u233?m y\u233?ngwafaretam f\u225? k\u233?t\u225?n Deifidefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Njam Uria nufary\u233?ng, Deifid\u233?m y\u233?motai f\u225? ndernaye Joab a fiyar\u233? kafrendaw\u233?t a ndernaye m\u233?k tiyotau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mo t\u233?mndang\u233? Uria, "N\u233?ng\u233?m m\u233?ngot a kenagh, Deifid\u233?m w\u233?i y\u233?ngwatembai ram\u233?gh rokar y\u225? Uriai y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? njam y\u233?mo y\u233?frangoi utman\u233?gh m\u233?ngo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
W\u233?nde Uria yau y\u233?ngmorm\u233?n m\u233?ngotuot. F\u225? y\u233?kmang\u233?rm\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? utman\u233?gh m\u233?ngon s\u233?safnefaf y\u233?n\u233? s\u233?mb\u225?r y\u233?maf\u233? warsagh \u225?roene utman\u233?gh m\u233?ngo wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?rf\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Njam Deifid n\u225?y\u225?rai nden\u233? Uria yau y\u233?ngmorm\u233?n m\u233?ngotuot, y\u233?mo y\u233?motai f\u225?, "N\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m k\u233?rt\u233?? N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m yau kangote m\u233?ngotuot s\u233?nonjo s\u233?mb\u225?r t\u225?f tekfifi k\u233?s k\u233?n\u233?syo?" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Uriam yangoi, n\u225?k boks Israil fiyar\u233? a Juda ekmang k\u233?t\u233? farai m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?n, a Joab a tane ndimbalafene \u225?r m\u233?ngo narametat k\u233?t\u233? m\u233? saf\u233?nro sifayan. Ndern\u225?ye y\u233?nd so kuwanon m\u233?ngot m\u233?n\u225?t w\u233?ri nu n\u233?net a njamke n\u233?net a k\u233?m\u233?gh\u233?t tane amafof\u233?? Y\u233?nd sote norayan nden\u233? y\u233?ndo y\u233?nd yam yau so ewafrotan."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Deifid\u233?m t\u233?mndang\u233? f\u225?, "W\u233?t n\u233?mor y\u233?na s\u233?nonjo efogh, a k\u225?ye f\u233?m t\u233?u nangota k\u233?t\u225?n fiyarafefaf." F\u233?yo Uria y\u233?morang\u233?rm\u233?n Jerusalemm\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? efghon a \u225?mb y\u233?namayo efghon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u233?yo Deifid\u233?m y\u233?nmumyoi f\u225? m\u233?n\u225?t n\u233?net a yiy\u225?toi w\u233?riaf\u233?. W\u233?nde yau Uria yumyoi s\u225?i kangotau m\u233?ngotuot y\u225?njo amafoefaf, w\u233?ikor f\u225? ekmang\u233?rm\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? utman\u233?gh m\u233?ngo s\u233?safnefaf y\u233?maf\u233? warsagh \u225?roene utman\u233?gh wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?rf\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Deifid\u233?m yam tafrendau m\u233?n\u225?t Uriane k\u233?rot
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
F\u233?yo \u225?mb akwan Deifid\u233?m y\u233?farotam f\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n Joabefaf a y\u233?ramai k\u233?t\u225?n Uriafaf m\u233?n\u225?t so taramangai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?rnan nden\u233? y\u233?ng\u233?mndai Joab, "T\u233?kmangi Uria fronde sifayan \u225?sm\u233?gh \u225?nde sotaf\u233? y\u233?m. F\u233?yo t\u233?nmango m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? so k\u233?rotio y\u233?smetat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u233?yo Joab\u233?m y\u233?kmai Uria y\u233?n\u233? sifayat ndimbal tesen mbakwfaf \u225?nde f\u225? mat t\u233?morw\u233?n m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?rafene muy\u233? k\u233?r ro \u225?r k\u225?smetaw\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
A njam m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r fiyar\u233? enmorm\u233?n n\u233?ntory\u233?nd k\u233?tam\u233? ndimbal tesenta m\u233?n\u225?t \u225?sm\u233?gh\u233?t, Uria Itait \u225?r y\u233?smay\u233?nd k\u233?rotio m\u233?rne y\u233?maf\u233? \u225?mb Israil fiyaraf\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
F\u233?yo Joab\u233?m y\u233?ngwatembai m\u233?km\u233?n ghan y\u225?faf Deifidefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Y\u233?mo y\u233?mndai y\u225?njo si r\u233?sagh \u225?r, "Y\u233?kayota m\u233?inyotio mat si m\u233?km\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n warsagh \u225?roefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
W\u233?nde f\u225? m\u233?t\u233? t\u225?f n\u233?kwaf\u233? n\u225?fgheta a kamotang\u233?, 'N\u233?mam\u233?n s\u233?fe tang\u233?m kaka fifi k\u233?t\u225?n ndimbal tesenfaf? Yau f\u225? mat tam nden\u233? so mbakwta enamndat? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
N\u233?m\u233? Abimelek Gideonene ambum y\u233?smetam\u233?nd k\u233?rotio k\u233?t\u233? Tebej y\u233?n\u233? amafam emofem t\u233?namndaw\u233?t w\u237?me f\u225? k\u233?tam\u233? mbakwta? N\u233?m\u233? f\u233?m kaka n\u233?ngaflay\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n mbakwfaf?' F\u233?yo taufro, 'Uria Itaitm\u233?n \u225?r t\u233? y\u233?smetam\u233?nd w\u233?i k\u233?rotio.'"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
F\u233?yo ghan t\u233?fn\u225?r y\u233?ngmorm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n Jerusalem a yaramai m\u233?inyotio yam ufroghm\u233?n y\u225? Deifide. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
F\u225? norayai, "M\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r n\u233?ntory\u233?ng t\u233?fe \u225?sm\u233?gh\u233?t fanfne sifayam\u233?, a njam y\u233?ndfem tangwifnaw\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n ndimbal tesen s\u233?safne fasafaf, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
tuk\u233?n efe t\u225?fayong\u233?rw\u233?n mbakwan fimbe t\u233?nmafy\u225?totaw\u233?t, \u225?mb warsagh \u225?r k\u233?rotio esmetam\u233?nd, f\u225? w\u233?i Uria Itaitm\u233?n \u225?r."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Deifid norayai, "Mer, taufro Joabe yau t\u225?f m\u225?m\u233? mwighayam. Witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? naifayam y\u233?s\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? s\u233?nonjo efghon a y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?s y\u233?m kaitam! Nasmetati minde \u225?mb efghon t\u225?f, a tanangi ndimbal tesen!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Njam Uriane amaf n\u225?y\u225?rai nden\u233? y\u225?njar k\u233?r t\u233? t\u233?m, y\u233?mo yeye tarametau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Njam y\u233?mon efogh nefoi, Deifid\u233?m engwafaretam Batsibafaf a y\u233?nmasroy\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n warsagh \u225?roene utman\u233?gh m\u233?ngot, a f\u225? n\u233?namndai \u225?mb amaf. F\u233?yo y\u233?mo y\u233?r\u225?ftam ghak\u233?r ambum. W\u233?nde m\u233?ndm\u233?nd t\u233?morw\u233?n y\u233?nayan n\u233?m\u233? Deifid\u233?m yafrotam.
