\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Natan\u233?m yus\u233?rmbotam Deifid
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
F\u233?yo Yuram yafretam Natan Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r m\u233?n\u225?t so Deifide tawaitotau y\u233?n\u233? si, "K\u233?t\u233? tarw\u233?n s\u243?mbio \u225?r ghak\u233?r \u225?mb tesenan. \u193?mb t\u233?morw\u233?n wemar, a \u225?mb t\u233?morw\u233?n yauyau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Wemar \u225?roene tamorw\u233?n t\u225?rf\u225?r ndimbal sif a kau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Oronjagh \u225?roene n\u233?m\u233? \u225?mb yau tamorw\u233?n w\u233?nde n\u233?mbnar sif tos\u233? y\u233?mo manie yanai. Y\u233?mo yanotam y\u233?n\u233? n\u233?mbnar sif tos\u233?, a f\u225? kanotaw\u233?t m\u233?rne y\u225?njo ambumaf\u233?. Y\u233?nayam njamke tanetau y\u233?n\u233? \u225?roene merekinan a nu tenetam y\u225?ne kafusiyan. Y\u233?mo tambnangai y\u225?njo ng\u225?ngaye ndenanit y\u225?ne fasri m\u233?r\u233?s. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
\u193?mb efghon wan t\u233?fn\u225?r nufary\u233?ng k\u233?t\u233? wemar \u225?roene m\u233?ngon. W\u233?nde siya t\u233?smangai y\u225?njoyo sif o kau, y\u233?mo yanan yauyau \u225?roene sif a y\u233?smai a y\u233?frendam y\u225?njo wan t\u233?fn\u225?rai."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Deifid namndai n\u233?kwaf\u233? a uny\u233?ghofnar si norayai, "Nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Yur\u233? k\u233?s nakete \u225?rk\u233? \u225?r emo njam yafrota nden\u233? yam so tanang\u233? k\u233?r! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u233?mo so fai tawangong\u233? 4 sif\u233? y\u225? yauyau \u225?roe y\u233?n\u233? \u225?mbiro y\u233?mo oroe k\u233?s yanai a m\u233?nam\u233?n yau yutmai."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u233?yo Natan n\u225?r\u225?yai Deifidfaf, "F\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r f\u233?n\u233?m! Yur\u233?, Israil \u225?rfene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, norayai: Y\u233?ndon n\u233?faghary\u233?n f\u233?m Israil \u225?rfene warsagh \u225?r a n\u233?manjary\u233?n k\u233?tam\u233? Solene waftata. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?ndon n\u233?maramay\u233?n f\u233?fene Yurane m\u233?ngo a y\u225?ne amaf k\u233?s em a Israil \u225?r lim\u225?ngh\u233?t a Juda. A y\u233?n\u233? yau njam em f\u233?yotarofnar, y\u233?ndon fai k\u233?maramangay\u233?n mindeyo, a mindefifi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
N\u233?mam\u233?n, w\u233?t, f\u233?mon m\u225?m\u225?fi tafrote Yurane si a tafrote y\u233?n\u233? merofnar yam? M\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mo t\u233? t\u233?smete Uria Itait \u225?r Amon \u225?rfene witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? naifaye a oroe yan\u233? y\u225?ne amaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Soram\u233? efghon, fene m\u233?r\u233?n so emo witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? nafayan m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mofem y\u233?nd t\u233? wasalita y\u233?naye k\u233?s yanang Uriane amaf fendio.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
"Nden\u233? Yur\u233? noraye: M\u233?nam\u233?n n\u233?m\u233? f\u233?mo yafrotam. Y\u233?ndon so t\u233?tyar\u233?n \u225?mb yam fene m\u233?rnan m\u233?n\u225?t yau so niy\u225?retan f\u233?m. Y\u233?ndon so erametan fene amaf k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mb \u225?rfefaf fene gh\u233?kfanyo, a f\u225? so ek\u233?m m\u233? saf\u233?n efandat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
F\u233?mo yafrotam kwankwane, w\u233?nde y\u233?ndo y\u233?n\u233? so ewafrotan s\u225?i nufrotat fefaf saf\u233?nro m\u233?inyotio Israil \u225?rfene s\u225?fan.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Deifid kafenau y\u225?njo k\u233?rtam\u233?n
