F\u233?yo Deifid kafenau Natanefaf, "Y\u233?nd t\u233? yaufiyam kufrotan Yurafaf.: Natan\u233?m yawangoi, "N\u233?m\u233?w\u233?t, w\u233?nde Yuram t\u233? n\u233?mawai fene, a f\u233?m yau so k\u233?r n\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? yaufiyamm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
W\u233?nde m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mo t\u233? yuyafo s\u233?nan\u233?gh tik\u233?f Yurai y\u233?naye y\u233?n\u233? siyafrotam, fene ambum so k\u233?r y\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Soram\u233? Natan n\u233?ngangotam y\u225?ne m\u233?ngot, Yuram y\u233?ngwafaretam k\u233?r yam k\u233?t\u225?n Deifidene ambum Uriane amaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Deifid\u233?m wamneng\u233?gh yafngoi Ng\u225?nj\u225?n m\u233?n\u225?t ambum gh\u233?rs\u233? m\u233? so t\u233?morw\u233?n. F\u225? nawafarmai njamkefnar a t\u233?kmang\u233?rw\u233?n s\u233?mb\u225?r saf\u233?n mbandan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
