F\u233?yo 7 efghon ambum k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n, Deifidene si w\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r f\u233?rf\u233?r tamorw\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i taufrongay\u233?nd a norayay\u233?nd, "f\u225? yau k\u225?y\u225?retau t\u225?f ambum njam enjne t\u233?m. N\u233?m\u233? m\u233?njtaye yam so y\u233?mo yafrote t\u225?f njam y\u233?ndfem taufrong\u233?m nden\u233? ambum k\u233?r t\u233? t\u233?m."
