Y\u225?ne si wawanjagh \u225?r tamorw\u233?n s\u233?lngw\u233?l a y\u233?mnday\u233?nd f\u225?, "Y\u233?ndfem yau kor n\u233?rsam f\u233?m. T\u225?f ambum njam m\u233? gh\u233?rs\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n, f\u233?m t\u233? kendau a nawanai njamke n\u233?net. W\u233?nde s\u233?nonjo t\u225?f ambum k\u233?r t\u233? t\u233?m, f\u233?m t\u233? n\u233?kmbo y\u233?ta a n\u233?ne w\u233?i enete."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Deifid\u233?m ewawangoi, "Y\u233?nd awafarmanwan kw\u233?m a kendan njam ambum m\u233? gh\u233?rs\u233? t\u233?m, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd norayay\u233?n, so Yur\u233? gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? y\u233?m tafaf a so tumyong\u233? ambum gh\u233?rs\u233? s\u225?i m\u233? y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
W\u233?nde n\u233?mam\u233?n y\u233?nd so nawafarmetan t\u225?f f\u225? k\u233?r t\u233? t\u233?m? So y\u233?ndon gh\u233?rsan kor f\u225? t\u233?nmangon? Y\u233?nd so w\u233?ng\u233?m \u225?mb efghon y\u225?faf, w\u233?nde f\u225? yau so n\u233?nangote tafaf."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
F\u233?yo Deifid\u233?m yamarotam Betsiba, y\u225?njo amaf, a takmarw\u233?n y\u233?maf\u233?. Betsiba n\u233?namndai ambum suaf\u233? a y\u233?r\u225?ftam ghak\u233?r ambum, a Deifid\u233?m y\u233?tkw\u233?n yaramai Solomon. Yuram tuwetau ambum, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
a y\u233?ngwafaretam si y\u225? k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r Natan nden\u233? y\u233?mofem so y\u233?tkw\u233?n taramangi Jedidia(y\u225?ne fifi "Yurane uw\u233?ghkaf"), nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Yuram ndernaye emndang.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Deifid\u233?m kw\u233?rnare yanai Raba
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Tekofnar, Joab\u233?f k\u225?smetaw\u233?t y\u233?maf\u233? Raba, ndimbal tesen Amon k\u233?nj\u250?n, a y\u233?mon kw\u233?rnare ewanai y\u233?fene ndimbal muyaf\u233? \u225?sm\u233?gh sifay\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Joab\u233?m ewafaretam siaf\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i taufrongay\u233?nd Deifide, "Y\u233?nd t\u233? k\u225?sm\u233?wam y\u233?maf\u233? Raba y\u233?nay\u233?n y\u225?ne nu sifay\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Y\u233?nam\u233? tanwasro m\u233?inyotio fiyar\u233? a kw\u233?rnare tanangi ndimbal tesen m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndo m\u233?t\u233? tanan a t\u233?ngwifon ambino t\u233?ngwaindang\u233?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
F\u233?yo Deifid\u233?m m\u233?inyotio fiyar\u233? eumendam a eyotam k\u233?t\u225?n Raba, a y\u233?maf\u233? n\u225?smetam\u233?nd a yanay\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Deifid\u233?m y\u233?nmanai warsagh \u225?roene \u225?kiki k\u233?tam\u233? y\u225?ne s\u233?nkota, a y\u233?fayoy\u233?nd k\u233?t\u233? y\u225?ne s\u233?nkoyan. \u193?kiki t\u233?morw\u233?n golm\u233?n wafroghm\u233?n a \u225?mb mer w\u237?maf\u233?, a y\u225?ne k\u233?rt\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n 75. Deifid\u233?m yanai ndimbal mani y\u233?tkw\u233?n m\u233?nayan m\u233?kan tanwarsaw\u233?t rokar k\u233?tam\u233? ndimbal tesenta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Y\u233?mo w\u233?i ey\u225?toi Rabam\u233?n \u225?r faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rot a tawafaretaw\u233?t f\u225? m\u233?n\u225?t so k\u225?s\u225?fotaw\u233?t m\u233?naye, soe, tot t\u233?f\u233?n fike, a tot t\u233?f\u233?n mbilaye, a s\u225?i k\u225?s\u225?fotaw\u233?t m\u233?nayan s\u233?mend ram\u233?ghan. Ndenaye y\u233?mo y\u233?n\u233? Amon tesenm\u233?n \u225?r tawafrotau. F\u233?yo Deifid a m\u233?inyotio fiyar\u233? kangotaw\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?n Jerusalem.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 13
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Amnon a Tamar
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Y\u233?na Deifidene ambum Absalom y\u225?ne y\u225?m\u233?r\u233?s t\u233?morw\u233?n y\u233?m\u233?ry\u233?nm\u233?raf\u233? k\u233?retau y\u233?tkw\u233?n t\u233?morw\u233?n Tamar. A Amnon y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?rsoene \u225?mb ghak\u233?r, m\u233?ndeyam yifoi y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?rsoefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Amnon n\u233?namndai minde m\u233?ndeyam yifoi Tamarfaf yaufiyamot, m\u233?r\u233?s t\u233?morw\u233?n \u225?rofnar a Amnon\u233?m m\u233?ndefnar y\u233?fandau Tamar.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
W\u233?nde Amnonene t\u233?morw\u233?n mwigh\u233? k\u233?r ro f\u250?tar-y\u225?ne \u225?mb afam\u233?n y\u225?nng\u233?n Jonadab. F\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n Deifidene y\u225?ngnoene Simiane. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
\u193?mb efghon Jonadab norayai k\u233?t\u225?n Amnonefaf, "N\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m k\u233?rt\u233?? N\u233?mam\u233?n so warsagh \u225?roene ambum n\u233?rete w\u225?iw\u225?iaf\u233? \u225?mb akwan \u225?mb akwan?" F\u233?yo Amnon\u233?m t\u233?mndang\u233? f\u225?, "Y\u233?ndo m\u233?nde yafrotan Tamarfaf, tane an\u233? Absalomene y\u225?m\u233?rsoefaf."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Jonadab norayai, "Mer, y\u233?ndo so k\u233?n\u233?mndan n\u233?m\u233? so yafrote, Nguwano k\u233?m\u233?gh sifayat t\u225?f a kun\u233?gh nden\u233? f\u233?m n\u233?m enjne. Njam feraf\u233? y\u233?n\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t fe fandagh\u233?t, t\u233?mota f\u225? m\u233?n\u225?t so t\u233?nmumyong\u233? Tamar so efrende \u225?mb njamke fe. T\u233?mnd\u233? f\u225? nden\u233? f\u233?m so mer t\u225?f kamnda njam y\u233?mo y\u233?frenda a y\u233?fanda a n\u233?mwawarmbeneta njamke y\u225?njo ng\u225?ngaye."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u233?yo Amnon n\u225?kmai nunyai kar enjne t\u233?morw\u233?n. A njam warsagh \u225?r y\u233?nmorm\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t y\u225? fandagh\u233?t. Amnon\u233?m yamnendai f\u225?, "Gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? t\u225?f y\u233?n\u233? tane m\u233?r\u233?s Tamar a y\u233?negha tane m\u233?ndef\u233? disan a so y\u233?fandan. A so t\u225?f y\u233?netan y\u225?ne ng\u225?ngam\u233?n." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u233?yo Deifid namyoi a y\u233?ngwafaretam Tamar k\u233?t\u225?n Amnonene m\u233?ngot m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tafrendau \u225?mb njamke y\u225?yot.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Njam Tamar nufary\u233?ng k\u233?t\u233? Amnonene m\u233?ngot, m\u233?r\u233?s y\u233?ngmorm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n f\u225? \u225?nde t\u233?kmang\u233?rw\u233?n a so t\u233?fandau y\u233?mo s\u225?i flaw\u233? t\u233?rm\u233?nau. F\u233?yo y\u233?mo y\u233?n\u233?gham m\u233?ndef\u233? disan y\u225?yot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
W\u233?nde njam m\u233?rsom freng\u233?gh yafngoi njamke wafligh t\u233?reyan y\u225? r\u233?re, f\u225? nakenai n\u233?net. Amnon\u233?m emndai y\u225?njo \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, "M\u233?inyotio \u225?r k\u233?tonangi y\u233?nam\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mo t\u233?mndang\u233? Tamar, "S\u233?nonjo t\u233?nman njamke k\u233?nj\u250?t y\u233?nan tane k\u233?m\u233?gh sifayat a kw\u233?mangjna y\u233?na." F\u233?yo tamam y\u233?ngwawanai y\u225?ne m\u233?ndef\u233? disaf\u233? y\u225?yot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
W\u233?nde t\u225?f m\u233?rsom njam t\u233?manjnau f\u225?. Y\u233?mo y\u233?rai a y\u233?mndai, k\u233?naf y\u233?nan k\u233?m\u233?gh\u233?t y\u233?ndf\u233?, tane m\u233?ndef\u233? m\u233?r\u233?s."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
F\u225? kutnang\u233?, "Yau, tane ghak\u233?r! Yau ong\u233?n n\u233?m mwighayan! Yau yafrota tafaf y\u233?n\u233?! Y\u233?n\u233? yaufiyam yau ewafrotat Israil\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
\u193?ndan so y\u233?nd w\u233?ng\u233?m t\u225?f tane w\u225?iw\u225?ie? A f\u233?m so \u225?mb ndimbal ong\u233?n \u225?r n\u233?manmotat Israil k\u233?nj\u250?n. Gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? m\u233? t\u225?f t\u233?mnda warsagh \u225?r y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n, a y\u233?mo so k\u233?mumyong\u233? f\u233?m kawerem y\u233?ndf\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
W\u233?nde Amnon\u233?m yau tiy\u225?retau m\u233?r\u233?s, a minde muyaf\u233? k\u233?s t\u233?morw\u233?n a m\u233?r\u233?s yau muyaf\u233?, y\u233?mo t\u233?roghau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?yo tekofnar Amnonene uw\u233?gh nawengoi m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat, a y\u233?mo m\u233?ndm\u233?ndaf\u233? yinjoi m\u233?r\u233?s yau kor nden\u233? fronde ndernaye minde m\u233?ndef\u233? yinjoi. K\u233?tor y\u233?nam\u233?! Y\u233?mo s\u233?ne y\u233?ngsotau m\u233?r\u233?s.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Tamar kutnang\u233?, "Yau, yau! S\u225?i y\u233?nd kwatemb s\u233?nonjo siy\u233?m minde m\u225?m\u225?fi n\u233?m\u233? f\u233?mo t\u233? tafrote tafaf." W\u233?nde Amnon yau yiy\u225?rai m\u233?r\u233?s. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
F\u225? nutnai y\u225?njo \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?rafefaf a ewamnendai, "T\u233?nmitangi y\u233?n\u233? amaf t\u233?ndot, a t\u233?ng\u233?mnangi f\u225?s\u225? y\u225? soram\u233?!" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
F\u233?yo \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r\u233?m t\u233?ndot y\u233?nmutory\u233?nd m\u233?r\u233?s a y\u233?mnay\u233?nd f\u225?s\u225? y\u225? s\u233?mta, m\u233?r\u233?s tawong\u233?rw\u233?n tomb\u233? s\u225?l\u225?me, t\u233?morw\u233?n t\u250?m\u233?n yam y\u233?n\u233? efghon y\u233?fe \u225?rofnar warsagh \u225?rfene m\u233?r\u233?s ambumat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
W\u233?nde s\u233?nonjo Tamar\u233?m y\u233?ft\u233?rar y\u225?njo s\u225?l\u225?me a ek\u233?m fak y\u225?njo s\u233?nkoyan. F\u233?yo y\u233?nam\u233?, y\u233?nayan y\u225?ne s\u225?f y\u225?ne ng\u225?ngayan t\u233?morw\u233?n, m\u233?r\u233?s n\u233?nwanoi kendau.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Y\u225?njo ghak\u233?r Absalom\u233?m yinjoi y\u225?m\u233?r\u233?s a y\u233?motai, "N\u233?m\u233? efalo y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m nden\u233? Amnonf\u233? f\u233?maf\u233? tare? Mer, tane m\u233?r\u233?s, m\u233?tar m\u233? s\u233?nonjo, f\u233?t\u233? fene ghak\u233?r t\u233?m, yau m\u225?m\u233? mwigh\u233? n\u233?m y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n." F\u233?yo Tamar t\u233?kmang\u233?rw\u233?n ndenanit s\u233?far\u233?kw amaf y\u225?ne ghak\u233?roene m\u233?ngon Absalom.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Njam warsagh \u225?r Deifid n\u225?y\u225?rai n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? nufrotam. F\u225? minde n\u233?kwaf\u233? n\u225?fetam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
A Absalom em \u225?mb yau t\u233?mndetau Amnon y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n, y\u233?mo m\u233?ndm\u233?ndaf\u233? t\u233?fandau mindefifi m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mo n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? yafrotam y\u225?m\u233?rsoefaf.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Absalom\u233?m fai yangotam Amnonefaf
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
S\u243?mbio y\u250?nj\u233?f soram\u233?, njam Absalomene sif s\u237?f n\u233?nfetaw\u233?t k\u233?t\u233? Baal-ajor Efraim kaka, Absalom\u233?m ewarawai m\u233?inyotio warsagh \u225?roene ambum m\u233?n\u225?t so tanmorw\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n t\u233?m\u233?ndfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
F\u225? y\u233?ngmorm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n warsagh \u225?roefaf a norayai, tane sif s\u237?f n\u233?f\u233?gh \u225?r sem \u225?s\u225?foghan em. So warsagh \u225?r a y\u225?ne \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rf\u233? en\u233?m gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t t\u233?m\u233?nd s\u225?i yafrotam y\u233?ndf\u233??
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Warsagh \u225?rom yawangoi, "Yau, tane ambum, njam y\u233?nd m\u233?inyotio t\u233?nmorw\u233?n y\u233?ndfem k\u233?maramangay\u233?m minde k\u233?rtaf\u233?." Absalom m\u233?njt\u233? m\u233? tafrotau w\u233?nde warsagh \u225?r yau y\u233?nmorm\u233?n ndemam\u233?n y\u233?ta f\u233?t\u233? yaramai Absalome freng\u233?gh.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Absalom norayai, "Mer, f\u233?t\u233?, njam yau f\u233?m n\u233?n\u233?m, ndernaye w\u233?t tane n\u233?ng\u233?n Amnon s\u225?i y\u233?nmafareta t\u233?fefaf?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Warsagh \u225?r namotai, "N\u233?mam\u233?n Amnon?" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
W\u233?nde m\u233? Absalom tauremnau warsagh \u225?r k\u233?t\u225?notio f\u225? namyoi m\u233?n\u225?t en\u233?umyoi m\u233?inyotio y\u225?njo ambum so tangmorw\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n, y\u233?mafayo Amnon. F\u233?yo Absalom\u233?m y\u233?frendam t\u233?m\u233?nd f\u233?yotaroyan y\u225? warsagh \u225?roe.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Absalom tamndang\u233? yanjo \u225?r, "Nawanjetati k\u233?t\u225?notio Amnon kor w\u233?riaf\u233? kamndang\u233?, f\u233?yo njam ng\u225?ngaye tawaunyan, t\u233?smangi t\u225?f k\u233?rotio! Yau t\u225?f f\u233?rf\u233?r em. Y\u233?ndonyo ewafareta. Mwigh\u233? t\u225?kmangi a yafrotati!" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
F\u233?yo Absalomene ng\u225?ng\u233? waun\u233?ghom y\u233?mofem k\u233?rotio y\u233?smetam\u233?nd Amnon. A \u225?mb ambum warsagh \u225?roene n\u225?tnam\u233?nd y\u233?fenjo osan a nawatembay\u233?nd.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Njam f\u225? kangotaw\u233? y\u233?fenjo endm\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n Jerusalem, y\u233?n\u233? ghanyam yiy\u225?njai Deifid: "Absalom\u233?m t\u233? k\u233?rotio t\u225?smete m\u233?inyotio warsagh \u225?roene ambum, yau \u225?mb gh\u233?rs\u233? nunjar!" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Warsagh \u225?r nokayoi, y\u233?tirary\u233?ng y\u225?njo s\u225?l\u225?me, a n\u233?nguyai f\u225?yo k\u233?t\u225?n mbandot. Y\u225?ne wawanjagh t\u233?fn\u225?r \u225?r\u233?m w\u233?i nden\u225?yo taft\u233?rnaw\u233?t y\u233?fenjo s\u225?l\u225?me m\u225?m\u233? gh\u233?raye yeyan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
W\u233?nde t\u225?f f\u233?t\u233? Jonadab, Deifid y\u225?nng\u233?noene ambumaf\u233? Simia, nufary\u233?ng a korayang\u233?, "Yau, yau t\u225?f efalo yiy\u225?totati nden\u233? m\u233?inyotio kar warsagh \u225?roene ambum esmetam\u233?nd! M\u233? f\u225?ro y\u233?morm\u233?n Amnon! Absalom\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? kwankwane mwigh\u233? t\u233?faronau k\u233?t\u225?mayo njam Amnon t\u233?ronghau a yaufoyam yafrotam y\u225?njo y\u225?m\u233?r\u233?s Tamar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
Yau, tane yur\u233? warsagh \u225?r, fene ambum yau m\u233?inyotio k\u233?r tam! M\u233? Amnonro t\u233?m." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Tekofnar Absalom n\u233?ngatnoi. F\u233?yo gh\u233?k\u233?f fayogh t\u233?fn\u225?ram k\u233?t\u233? Jerusalem araketa ewinjoi t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?newonaw\u233?t tunak\u233?f y\u233?n\u233? end kar\u233?fta mbormbor tamb\u233?n, F\u225? nengoi m\u233?n\u225?t so taufrongai warsagh \u225?roe." Y\u233?ndo efandan \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n en\u233?m k\u233?tam\u233? Oronaim endm\u233? mband tunak\u233?f t\u233?ndom\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
Jonadab\u233?m t\u233?mndang\u233? warsagh \u225?r, "K\u233?reta! K\u233?t\u233? k\u233?s em! Warsagh \u225?roene ambum en\u233?m, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?nd y\u233?nai norayan."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
F\u225? tekofnar nufary\u233?nd, ye k\u233?naw\u233?t ndimbal k\u233?r\u225?ye, f\u233?yo warsagh \u225?r a y\u225?ne m\u233?inyotio \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r ye m\u225?m\u233? gh\u233?rare m\u233?ndm\u233?nd y\u233?maf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
A Deifid nendam t\u225?rf\u225?r efogh y\u225?njo ambumm\u233?n Amnon. Absalom nawatembai y\u225?kiefaf, f\u225? Taimai Amiudene ambum, warsagh \u225?r Gesurm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
F\u233?yo warsagh \u225?r Deifid, y\u233?nam\u233? nafenam Amnonene k\u233?rm\u233?n, karonjagh m\u233?n\u225?t fifian so kakayeyay\u233?nd y\u225?njo ambumaf\u233? Absalom. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
A warsagh \u225?r Deifid, s\u233?nonjo mat t\u233?morw\u233?n Amnonene k\u233?r, m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n y\u233?fandagh y\u225?ne ambum Absalom.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 14
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Joab\u233?m end t\u233?frendau m\u233?n\u225?t Absalom so k\u233?nangotau
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Joab mat n\u225?y\u225?toi minde k\u233?r\u225?ye karonjagh m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tinjongai Absalom. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?ngwatembai si amafot k\u233?t\u225?mam\u233?n Tekoa endene t\u233?morw\u233?n mer yam k\u233?t\u225?n k\u225?fet\u233? mwighafaf. Y\u233?mo y\u233?mndai amaf, "Kuine nden\u233? f\u233?m kar yeyan n\u233?m nawota y\u233?mon s\u225?l\u225?me a yau n\u225?y\u225?tota mer w\u233?kwere. Nden\u233? yame a nuinda amaf efe t\u233? ye kawaramete k\u233?r \u225?roe tekfifi efogh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u233?yo kuwano k\u233?t\u225?n warsagh \u225?roefaf a yaufrota amaf\u233? n\u233?m\u233? so korayangai.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Njam amaf k\u233?tamam\u233?n Tekoam\u233?n y\u233?ngwanetam warsagh \u225?r, amaf y\u225?wefnoi s\u225?f mbandot ndimbal utman\u233?ghaf\u233? a nutnai o warsagh \u225?r! Kw\u225?ut\u225?na ta!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Warsagh \u225?r namotai, "N\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m k\u233?rt\u233??"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Amafom yawangoi, "Wa, y\u233?nd w\u233?m s\u233?far\u233?kw! Tane t\u233? k\u233?r t\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Tane s\u243?mbio ambum k\u225?sm\u233?t k\u233?t\u233? ndau sifayan. Efe \u225?mb yau k\u233?t\u233? t\u233?m k\u233?mbogh\u233?t \u225?mb y\u233?morm\u233?n y\u233?smetam k\u233?rotio. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
S\u233?nonjo m\u233?inyotio m\u233?r\u233?n faiot nomnendat, t\u233?feyot so y\u233?m fene ambum. Y\u233?ndfem so y\u233?smetam m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mo t\u233? y\u233?smetam y\u225?nng\u233?n, y\u233?mo yau so tanang\u233? \u225?mb rokar y\u225?ne m\u233?rnafene rokarta. F\u225? m\u233?nde em s\u225?i tifongi y\u233?nar Kol y\u233?ndo \u225?rk\u233? noron, a tane \u225?roene y\u233?tkw\u233?n a tane m\u233?r\u233?n so kolindangi y\u233?n\u233? mband."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Warsagh \u225?rom y\u233?mndai, "Korong tafaf. Ngangota m\u233?ngot a y\u233?ndon m\u233? so y\u233?fandan \u225?mb \u225?rom yau so tiy\u225?njang\u233? f\u225?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Tekoam\u233?n amafom yawangoi, "O, k\u225?njo fe, tane yur\u233? warsagh \u225?r. Njam f\u233?m n\u233?masalitat m\u233?nam\u233?n tane w\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?ghm\u233?n, y\u233?nd t\u233?u t\u233?fnot w\u233?m a tane afane m\u233?ngo, a warsagh \u225?r a y\u225?ne lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? so y\u233?m t\u233?fnofnar."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Warsagh \u225?r norayai t\u233?nmasrongi tafaf, "Njam em t\u233?f\u233?n yufana. T\u233?nmasrongi tafaf, y\u233?ndo so mat k\u233?ny\u225?ton f\u233?m f\u225? yau so nawatarne w\u233?ikor!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
F\u233?yo amaf korayang\u233?, "Gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? waftaf\u233? koraya tafaf fene Yur\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene y\u233?tkw\u233?nan m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?mo yau so tumyo \u225?mb \u225?r fai s\u225?i yangota tane ambumoefaf, y\u233?nd m\u233?ndefnar w\u233?m \u225?mb f\u233?r\u233?k s\u225?i nerta."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?mo yawangoi, "Njamandio Yur\u233? nakete, yau so \u225?mb s\u237?f fene ambumoene s\u233?nkoyan tawas\u233?rmbotangi!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Amaf korayang\u233?, "Gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? kumyo y\u233?nd \u225?mbiro yam s\u225?i kamotang\u233?n tane yur\u233? a warsagh \u225?r."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?mo tumyong\u233?, "F\u233?yotaro koraya."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Amafom tawangong\u233?, "N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?mo kor yau ewawafrote y\u233?fe Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?r\u233?t nden\u233? f\u233?mo k\u233?s uny\u233?ghofnar si norayai tayayot wafrogh\u233?t? F\u233?monyo t\u233? n\u225?y\u225?to y\u233?n\u233? si farorghan, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m t\u233? nakena m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i t\u233?n\u233?mnjau fene ambino watemb\u233?gh\u233?t ambum. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
M\u233?inyotio y\u233?nd so k\u233?r y\u233?n\u233?m t\u233?fene gh\u233?rs\u233? sem ndenanit em nu y\u233?nau kasurng\u233? mbandot \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? yau w\u233?i kor so tan\u233?umenda. W\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yau m\u233? tasamburng\u233? gh\u233?rs\u233? ndetro. W\u233?nde y\u233?mo ewafrote end m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i y\u233?nmangota njam y\u233?nd kafalong\u233?m y\u225? tamb\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
"Y\u233?nd t\u233? kw\u233?n\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?nd s\u225?i noraiwam tane yuraf\u233? a warsagh \u225?r m\u233?nam\u233?n \u225?r\u233?m t\u233? kus\u233?mbotat y\u233?nd. Y\u233?nd norayang\u233?n tanjo k\u233?nj\u250?n, t\u225?f njam t\u233? warsagh \u225?r n\u225?y\u225?reta tafaf {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
a t\u233?nmanjarng\u233? y\u233?nd y\u233?feta emofem so t\u233?n\u233?ufangi k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? rokar \u225?rk\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?nmaramai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
N\u233?m\u233?w\u233?t, tane yur\u233? a warsagh \u225?rom so krufr\u225?t mwigh\u233? t\u233?nmaramang\u233? w\u233?ikor, 'Y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m nden\u233? f\u233?m ndenanit em Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene njafar so r\u233?sagh \u225?r y\u225?yamngotati mer k\u233?tam\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fita. So y\u233?m Yur\u233? f\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n f\u233?fefaf."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Warsagh \u225?rom yawangoi, "Y\u233?nd so mat w\u233?m \u225?mbiro yamm\u233?n a w\u233?t kwaufro efaloe."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Amaf n\u233?nwangoi, "N\u233?m\u233?w\u233?t, tane yur\u233? a warsagh \u225?r."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
"T\u233? Joab\u233?m n\u233?nk\u233?m f\u233?m y\u233?nan. F\u233?yo amafom yawangoi "Tane yur\u233? warsagh \u225?r ndernaye y\u233?nd so kakenang\u233?n? \u193?rk\u233? \u225?rom so t\u233?tnong\u233? \u225?mb rokar k\u233?tam\u233? fe tamb\u233?n. N\u233?m\u233?w\u233?t, Joab\u233?m y\u233?nd w\u233?nmafaretam a w\u233?mndai n\u233?m\u233? so norayai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Y\u233?mo yafrotam y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t so t\u233?kmangai k\u233?rt\u233? fe r\u233?re f\u233?nat\u233? kwayagh\u233?t, w\u233?nde f\u233?m n\u233?m mwigh\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?rnit a f\u233?m n\u233?m m\u233?inyotio yamm\u233?n nufrotat t\u233?fefaf!
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
F\u233?yo warsagh \u225?rom y\u233?ngwafaretam y\u225?faf Joab a yafroi y\u225?, "M\u233?inyotio mer y\u233?m, eng\u233?m t\u233?nmangongi tot\u233?r ambum Absalom."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Joab niyai yanjo s\u225?fe mbandot k\u233?njkam utman\u233?ghaf\u233? a norayai, "Y\u233?na soramafifi y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m nden\u233? y\u233?ndo t\u233? yanan fene mwigh\u233? faror\u233?gh tane yur\u233? warsagh \u225?r m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mo y\u233?frenda ta y\u233?n\u233? wafrogh\u233?t!
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
F\u233?yo Joab nuwanoi k\u233?t\u225?n Gesur a y\u233?nmasroi Absalom k\u233?t\u225?n Jerusalem. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
W\u233?nde warsagh \u225?rom y\u233?ramai y\u233?n\u233? wafar\u233?gh si, Absalom t\u233?u y\u233?ng\u233?m y\u225?ne m\u233?ngot, w\u233?nde f\u225? yau t\u225?f y\u233?n\u233?m tane s\u225?fan." F\u233?yo Absalom\u233?m yau yinjoi warsagh \u225?r.
