F\u233?m mat n\u233?m fene af\u233? a \u225?r k\u233?s. F\u225? m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r tamorw\u233?n. S\u233?nonjo f\u225? ndenanit n\u233?kwaf\u233? em beafene y\u233?fetm\u233? efe t\u233? oro yafrotam\u233?nd m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?ne tosam\u233?n. A nawafarota nden\u233? fene feraf\u233? mat \u225?r y\u233?m m\u233?km\u233?n. Y\u233?mo yau so y\u233?rse s\u233?mb\u225?r tek fiyaraf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
