F\u233?yo Deifid\u233?m emndai f\u225? m\u233?n\u225?t so t\u233?mndangay\u233?nd Amasa, "Nden\u233? f\u233?m em taneyo fifi, a f\u233?r\u233?k, Joab, t\u233?u Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam kw\u233?smang\u233? y\u233?nd k\u233?rotio y\u233?ndo yau njam f\u233?m k\u233?nkafan siya n\u233?m tane fiyar\u233? wafar\u233?gh s\u233?nko \u225?r y\u225?ne utman\u233?gh m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?n."
