Y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m nder\u233? ndimbale y\u233?ndo yaufiyam tafrotan. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan y\u233?nd kw\u233?n\u233?m y\u233?nau s\u233?nonjo, frondefifi \u225?r m\u233?inyotio Israil \u225?r k\u233?nj\u250?n nden\u233? y\u233?snetang\u233?n tane yur\u233? warsagh \u225?r."
